 level <em>26</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Critical Hits heal you and your pets for up to <span class="d3-color-green">21457</span> Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> Critical Hit Chance for each enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards while under the effects of Battle Rage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Deal damage equal to <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of your recent Critical Hits to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards every <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1482646276,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1482646276\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Fury</p><p>Enter a rage which increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> and Critical Hit Chance by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span>. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Tactics</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},calloftheancients:{a:'<p>Each point of Fury you spend heals you and your Ancients for <span class="d3-color-green">966</span> Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The Ancients deal <span class="d3-color-green">540%</span> weapon damage as Fire with each attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Fury every time an Ancient deals damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies hit by the Ancients are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds and have <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> increased chance to be Critically Hit.</p><p>The Ancients\' damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of all damage dealt to you is instead divided evenly between the Ancients.</p><p>The Ancients\' damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"col",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:254801712,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/254801712\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>Summon the ancient Barbarians Talic, Korlic, and Madawc to fight alongside you for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds. Each deals <span class="d3-color-green">270%</span> weapon damage per swing in addition to bonus abilities.</p><p><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Talic wields a sword and shield and uses Whirlwind and Leap.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Korlic wields a massive polearm and uses Cleave and Furious Charge.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Madawc dual-wields axes and uses Weapon Throw and Seismic Slam.</p> <p class="special">Rage</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},cleave:{a:'<p>Swing at all enemies around you and increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">235%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies cleaved are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> and take <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> increased damage from all sources for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Cleave\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',c:'<p>On Critical Hits, knock enemies up into the air and deal <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage to enemies where they land.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Generate <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> additional Fury per enemy hit.</p><p>Cleave\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies slain by Cleave explode, causing <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:568487545,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/568487545\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Fury per attack</p><p>Swing your weapon in a wide arc to deal <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage to all enemies caught in the swing.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},earthquake:{a:'<p>Increase Earthquake\'s damage to <span class="d3-color-green">6000%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-green">20</span> secondary tremors follow your movement and deal <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire each.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Create an icy patch, causing Earthquake to <span class="d3-color-green">Freeze</span> all enemies hit and deal Cold damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Remove the Fury cost and reduce the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p><p>Earthquake\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',e:'<p>All enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards are pulled in towards you.</p><p>Earthquake\'s damage turns into Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"fir"},icon:3857249268,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3857249268\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Fury<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds</p><p>Shake the ground violently, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">4800%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Rage</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},frenzy:{a:'<p>Each Frenzy effect also increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">2.5%</span>.</p><p>Frenzy\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Each strike has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to throw a piercing axe at a nearby enemy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Cold to all enemies in its path.</p><p>Frenzy\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> movement speed for each stack of Frenzy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Each hit has a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance to call down a bolt of lightning from above, stunning the enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase Fury generated to <span class="d3-color-green">6</span>.</p><p>Frenzy\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2975039367,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2975039367\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Fury per attack</p><p>Swing for <span class="d3-color-green">220%</span> weapon damage. Frenzy\'s attack speed increases by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds with each swing. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},furiouscharge:{a:'<p>Increase the damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1050%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Store up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> charges of Furious Charge.</p><p>Furious Charge\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',c:'<p>All enemies hit are <span class="d3-color-green">Frozen</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2.5</span> seconds.</p><p>Furious Charge\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Generate <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> additional Fury for each enemy hit while charging.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Recharge time is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds for every enemy hit. This effect can reduce the recharge time by up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3148293472,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3148293472\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Charge<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Fury</p><p>Rush forward knocking back and dealing <span class="d3-color-green">600%</span> weapon damage to enemies along your path.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">You gain a charge every <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds and can have up to <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> charge stored at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Might</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},groundstomp:{a:'<p>Enemies in the area also take <span class="d3-color-green">575%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the area of effect to <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards. Enemies are pulled closer before the strike lands.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies hit have a chance to drop a health globe.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase Fury generated to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Reduce the cooldown of Ground Stomp to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p><p>Enemies in the area have their movement speed slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds after they recover from being stunned.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:3010331147,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3010331147\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Fury<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds</p><p>Smash the ground, stunning all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},hammeroftheancients:{a:'<p>Smash for <span class="d3-color-green">640%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Create a shockwave that deals <span class="d3-color-green">505%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">22</span> yards in front of you.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each hit creates a tremor at the point of impact for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds that <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p><p>Hammer of the Ancients\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Critical Hits heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> of your maximum Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When you kill an enemy with Hammer of the Ancients, other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards are Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Hammer of the Ancients turns into Lightning damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:428781230,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/428781230\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Fury</p><p>Call forth a massive hammer to smash enemies directly in front of you for <span class="d3-color-green">535%</span> weapon damage. Hammer of the Ancients has a <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> increased Critical Hit Chance for every <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Fury that you have.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},ignorepain:{a:'<p>Instantly heal for <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> of maximum Life when activating Ignore Pain.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase duration to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Allies within <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> yards also gain <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> damage reduction and <span class="d3-color-green">Immunity</span> to control-impairing effects for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',d:'<p>While Ignore Pain is active, gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> increased movement speed and knock enemies away as you run.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',e:'<p>While Ignore Pain is active, gain <span class="d3-color-green">5364</span> Life per Fury spent.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2993679893,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2993679893\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Reduce all damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> and gain <span class="d3-color-green">Immunity</span> to all control-impairing effects for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},leap:{a:'<p>Shockwaves burst forth from the ground increasing the radius of effect to <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> yards and pulling affected enemies towards you.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the damage of Leap to <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> and send enemies hurtling away from where you land.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>You leap with such great force that enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards of the takeoff point take <span class="d3-color-green">180%</span> weapon damage and are also slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> additional Armor for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after landing.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Land with such force that enemies have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:832433827,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/832433827\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Fury<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds</p><p>Leap into the air, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">180%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards of your destination and slowing their movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},overpower:{a:'<p>Your Critical Hit Chance is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>Overpower\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Throw up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> axes at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">760%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Generate <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Fury for each enemy hit by Overpower.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Redirect <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> of incoming melee damage back to the attacker for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after Overpower is activated.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2462707378,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2462707378\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds</p><p>Deal <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> yards.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Critical Hits have a chance to reduce the cooldown of Overpower by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</span></p> <p class="special">Might</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},rend:{a:'<p>Increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1350%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the range of Rend to hit all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards.</p><p>Rend\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Affected enemies are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> and take <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> increased damage from all sources.</p><p>Rend\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Heal for <span class="d3-color-green">0.5%</span> of your maximum Life per second for each affected enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies killed while bleeding cause all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards to begin bleeding for <span class="d3-color-green">1100%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3772894290,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3772894290\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Fury</p><p>A sweeping strike causes all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards to Bleed for <span class="d3-color-green">1100%