r-green">20%</span><br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Movement Speed: <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span></p> <p class="special">Rage</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.barbarian={animosity:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/285471987\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase all Fury generation by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.<br/>Increase maximum Fury by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span>.</p><p>Fury is used to fuel your most powerful attacks.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"While most orders teach the merits of calming the seas of the soul, the guardians of Arreat have embraced the raging inner storm." —Chronicler Arlavoc</div> </div>',berserkerrage:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1163801070\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> additional damage while near maximum Fury.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"You wouldn\'t like me when I\'m angry." —Bannar the Berserker</div> </div>',bloodthirst:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1903569166\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Each point of Fury spent heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">966</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Compassion is weakness. To press the advantage when an opponent calls for mercy is the way of true power." —Halaberd the Conqueror</div> </div>',boonofbulkathos:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3861319589\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce the cooldowns of your:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Earthquake by <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Call of the Ancients by <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Wrath of the Berserker by <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The aid of the Immortal King shall come to those who have earned it.</div> </div>',brawler:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2654889491\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>As long as there are <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards, all of your damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I have two blades, one for each of you." —Blademaster Kharne</div> </div>',earthenmight:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4227302271\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Fury when Avalanche or Earthquake is triggered.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"My capital has become the cell in which I await my execution. The ground roars beneath me, announcing the presence of the wild men, as they rend and tear the foundations of the world and laugh. Oh, woe is me that I ever confused their savage ways for weakness."—Loren, Panep of Samauren</div> </div>',inspiringpresence:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1602331770\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The duration of your shouts is doubled. After using a shout you and all allies within <span class="d3-color-green">100</span> yards regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> of maximum Life per second for <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds.</p><p>Your shouts are:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Battle Rage<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Threatening Shout<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> War Cry</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The enemy poured through the gap until Warmaster Karja impaled three demons at once on our battle standard, tossing their corpses into the fray below as she roared a rallying call from high atop the battlements." —The Battle of the Starless Night</div> </div>',juggernaut:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3986096901\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The duration of control-impairing effects on you are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>. In addition, whenever a Stun, Freeze, Fear, or Immobilize is cast on you, you have a chance to recover <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of your maximum Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I swear to you, we put a dozen arrows into him and he just stood back up. These so-called barbarians, these madmen of the north—there is no stopping them." —Soldier of Bastion\'s Keep</div> </div>',nervesofsteel:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1851298116\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Fatal damage instead reduces you to <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> Life. For <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds afterward, you take <span class="d3-color-green">95%</span> reduced damage and are immune to all control-impairing effects.</p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The trials begin with childhood; skinning ferocious beasts, climbing windswept cliffs and carrying weapons heavy enough to make a southern soldier weep. Is it any wonder that they never give ground?" —Sir Aric of Duncraig</div> </div>',noescape:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3806796321\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of Weapon Throw, Seismic Slam, Ancient Spear, and Avalanche by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> against enemies more than <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards away from you.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Run if you must, but you\'ll only die tired." —Ooron Goons</div> </div>',poundofflesh:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/165667404\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you are healed by a health globe, gain <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> Life regeneration per second and <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span> increased movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds. This bonus stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"When the sky bleeds, the crops grow tall. When our enemies bleed, we grow strong." —Chant of the Harvest</div> </div>',rampage:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3639143356\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase Strength by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds after killing or assisting in killing an enemy. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The battle was never ending, sapping our minds and bodies to the point of exhaustion. But they thrived amidst the carnage, every killing blow renewing their bloodlust. They couldn\'t be stopped." —Sergeant Peshkov on the Siege of the Barbarians, 1123 Anno Kehjistani </div> </div>',relentless:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3881736131\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While below <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> Life, all skills cost <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> less Fury, Life per Fury Spent is doubled, and all damage taken is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">No matter the odds, some warriors simply refuse to fall.</div> </div>',ruthless:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2335019540\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> additional damage to enemies below <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The clans each paint their warriors in their own unique way. Some celebrate the mountain, others honor the fire, but the Targos clan worships the purifying virtue of pain.</div> </div>',superstition:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1939325266\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce all non-Physical damage by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>. When you take damage from a ranged or elemental attack, you have a chance to gain <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Fury.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The sorcery of the west has brought us nothing but blight. Strength built these walls, and strength will hold them." —Gruchac Hammerhand</div> </div>',swordandboard:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4291698953\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While wielding a shield, reduce all damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> and reduce Fury costs by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Turning away the attack of an enemy saps their resolve as surely as landing a blow of your own." —Battlemaster Kal-Jor</div> </div>',toughasnails:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2733948428\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase Armor by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.<br/>Increase Thorns by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">After a while the scars serve as their own layer of armor.</div> </div>',unforgiving:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3392231032\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You no longer degenerate Fury. Instead, you generate <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Fury every <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"It was as if he suddenly came to know every grievous injury endured by his ancestors, and he had selected that very moment to exact their collective revenge." —Chronicler Arlavoc</div> </div>',weaponsmaster:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3617945175\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain a bonus based on the weapon type of your main hand weapon:<br/>Swords/Daggers: <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased damage<br/>Maces/Axes: <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> Critical Hit Chance<br/>Polearms/Spears: <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> attack speed<br/>Mighty Weapons: <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Fury per hit</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"My men ambushed the traveler in the woods, but it was we who were surprised. Such keen senses, swift motions, flawless strikes. We never stood a chance." —Redjack the Bandit</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.crusader={akaratschampion:{a:'<p>Dealing damage burns enemies with the power of Akarat, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">460%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increases the bonus Wrath regeneration from Akarat\'s Champion to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Using Akarat\'s Champion reduces the remaining cooldown of your other abilities by <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> additional Armor while Akarat\'s Champion is active.</p><p>The first time you take fatal damage while Akarat\'s Champion is active, you will be returned to full health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased attack speed while Akarat\'s Champion is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"fir"},icon:3024819679,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3024819679\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">90</span> seconds</p><p>Explode with the power of your order, increasing your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> and increasing your Wrath regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},blessedhammer:{a:'<p>The hammer is engulfed in fire and has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to scorch the ground over which it passes. Enemies who pass through the scorched ground take <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> weapon damage as Fire per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The hammer is charged with lightning that occasionally arcs between you and the hammer as it spirals through the air, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to enemies caught in the arcs. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the damage of Blessed Hammer to <span class="d3-color-green">640%</span> weapon damage as Holy and increase its area of effect by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The hammer Slows enemies it passes through and has a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to explode on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">460%</span> weapon damage as Physical and Stunning enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The Hammer now orbits you as you move.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"hol",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:2047437116,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2047437116\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Wrath</p><p>Summon a blessed hammer that spins around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">320%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies hit.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},blessedshield:{a:'<p>The shield becomes charged with lightning and has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to Stun the first enemy hit for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds. Each enemy hit after the first has a <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> reduced chance to be Stunned.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The shield erupts in flames and has a <span class="d3-color-green">33%</span> chance to explode on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">310%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When the shield hits an enemy, your Armor is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> and Life regeneration is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When the shield hits an enemy, it splits into <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> small fragments that bounce between nearby enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">170%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The shield no longer bounces, but pierces through all enemies with a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to knock them aside.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:3505549997,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3505549997\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Wrath</p><p>Hurl your shield, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">430%</span> weapon damage as Holy plus <span class="d3-color-green">250%</span> of shield Block Chance as Holy damage. The shield will ricochet to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> nearby enemies.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bombardment:{a:'<p>In place of the burning spheres, barrels of spikes are hurled. Damage of each barrel is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> of your Thorns.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Each impact has a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> Critical Hit Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each impact scatters <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> mines onto the battlefield that explode when enemies walk near them, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',d:'<p>A single, much larger ball of explosive pitch is hurled at the targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">3320%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of randomly finding targets nearby, the bombardment will continue to fall on your initial target.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>70</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:1417711558,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1417711558\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds</p><p>Call in an assault from afar, raining <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> spheres of burning pitch and stone onto enemies around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2850%</span> total weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards of the impact zone.</p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},condemn:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of all damage taken while the explosion is building is added to the damage of the explosion.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>As the explosion charges up, it sucks in enemies. The closer it is to exploding, the more enemies it sucks in.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Reduce the cooldown by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second for each enemy hit by the explosion.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the damage radius to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The explosion now unleashes instantly.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:3346730045,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3346730045\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Build up a massive explosion, unleashing it after <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1160%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},consecration:{a:'<p>The edge of the consecrated ground is surrounded by a sacred shield, preventing enemies from moving through it.</p><p>The duration of the consecration is reduced to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The consecrated ground becomes covered in nails. Enemies that walk into the area take <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your Thorns damage every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the radius of the consecrated ground to <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards and increase the amount you and your allies heal for to <span class="d3-color-green">48278</span> Life per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies standing on consecrated ground take <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage as Fire per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies standing on consecrated ground have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to be Feared for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"phy",c:"hol",d:"fir",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:663260264,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/663260264\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Consecrate the ground <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards around you for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds. You and your allies heal for <span class="d3-color-green">32185</span> Life per second while standing on the consecrated ground.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fallingsword:{a:'<p>The ground you fall on becomes superheated for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">310%</span> weapon damage as Fire per second to all enemies who pass over it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',b:'<p>You build a storm of lightning as you fall which covers the area you land on for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Lightning strikes random enemies under the cloud, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">605%</span> weapon damage as Lightning and Stunning them for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',c:'<p>You land with such force that <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Avatars of the Order are summoned forth to fight by your side for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Each Avatar attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">280%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cooldown by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second for each enemy hit by Falling Sword.  The cooldown cannot be reduced below <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',e:'<p>A flurry of swords is summoned at the impact location, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">230%</span> weapon damage as Holy, hurling enemies around and incapacitating them for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:2440240234,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2440240234\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Wrath<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Launch yourself into the heavens and come crashing down on your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1700%</span> weapon damage to everything within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards of where you land.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fistoftheheavens:{a:'<p>Summon a fiery storm that covers a <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yard radius for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage as Fire every second to enemies who pass underneath it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The bolt detonates with a shockwave on impact, causing all enemies hit to be knocked away from the blast and Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Creates a fissure of lightning energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">410%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to nearby enemies. If there is another fissure nearby, lightning will arc between them dealing an additional <span class="d3-color-green">135%</span> weapon damage as Lightning with each arc.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The holy bolts crackle with holy lightning and zap enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards as they travel, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Hurl a fist of Holy power that pierces through your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">270%</span> weapon damage as Holy, and exploding at your target, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">435%</span> weapon damage as Holy to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p><p>The explosion creates <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> piercing charged bolts that crawl outward, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage as Holy to enemies through whom they pass.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"lit"},icon:3114805186,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3114805186\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Call forth a pillar of lightning from the heavens that explodes, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">545%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to any enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards. The explosion creates <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> piercing charged bolts that arc outward and deal <span class="d3-color-green">255%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},heavensfury:{a:'<p>The ray of Holy power grows to encompass <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2766%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to enemies caught within it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The ground touched by the ray becomes blessed, scorching it and dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1550%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to enemies who walks through.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The ray splits into <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> smaller beams, each dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1980%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Ground touched by the ray pulses with power for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds, stopping enemies who try to pass over it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Call down a furious ray of Holy power that is focused through you in a beam across the battlefield, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">960%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies it hits.</p><p>The cooldown is removed. Now costs <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Wrath.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:2946852966,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2946852966\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds</p><p>Call down a furious ray of Holy power that deals <span class="d3-color-green">1710%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to all enemies caught within it.</p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},ironskin:{a:'<p>Your metal skin is electrified, giving you a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to Stun enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When Iron Skin expires the metal explodes off, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1400%</span> weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>While active, your Thorns is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',e:'<p>If you take damage while Iron Skin is active, your movement speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds and you can move through enemies unhindered.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:3165782921,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3165782921\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Your skin turns to iron, absorbing <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of all incoming damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},judgment:{a:'<p>For every enemy upon whom you pass judgment, you heal for <span class="d3-color-green">2682</span> Life per second for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',b:'<p>All enemies are drawn toward the center of the judged area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the duration of the Immobilize to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Damage dealt to judged enemies has an <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased chance to be a Critical Hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies in the judged area deal <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> reduced damage for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2747472303,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2747472303\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds</p><p>Pass judgment on all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards of the targeted location, Immobilizing them in place for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},justice:{a:'<p>Hurl a sword of justice at your enemies. When the sword hits an enemy, gain <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When the hammer hits an enemy, there is an <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance it will crack into <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> smaller hammers that fly out and deal <span class="d3-color-green">245%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The hammer seeks out nearby targets and deal <span class="d3-color-green">335%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The hammer is charged with lightning and explodes on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards. Enemies caught in the explosion have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Throw a bolt of holy power that heals you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">2146</span> - <span class="d3-color-green">3219</span> Life when it hits an enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:1031678231,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1031678231\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Hurl a hammer of justice at your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">245%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lawsofhope:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases movement speed for you and your allies by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>, and allows everyone affected to run through enemies unimpeded.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases the maximum Life of you and your allies by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also reduces all Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also heals you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">1073</span> Life for every point of Wrath that you spend. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also reduces all non-Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3072384440,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3072384440\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empower the Law, surrounding you and your allies in a shield for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds that absorbs up to <span class="d3-color-green">124128</span> damage.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Recite the Law, healing you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">10728</span> Life per second.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Law may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Laws</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lawsofjustice:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also redirects <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of the damage taken by your allies to you for the next <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases Armor for you and your allies by <span class="d3-color-green">7000</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also surrounds you and your allies with shields of faith for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. The shields absorb up to <span class="d3-color-green">26821</span> damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> While the Law is empowered, any enemy who attacks you or your allies will have their damage reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds, stacking up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also grants immunity to control impairing effects to you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2430907811,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2430907811\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empower the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">490</span> increased resistance to all elements for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Recite the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">140</span> increased resistance to all elements.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Law may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Laws</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lawsofvalor:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases your Life on Hit by <span class="d3-color-green">21457</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also grants you a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to Stun all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases your Critical Hit Damage by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the law also reduces the Wrath cost of all skills by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> While the Law is empowered, each enemy killed increases the duration by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds of increased time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3531549488,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3531549488\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empower the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased Attack Speed for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Recite the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased Attack Speed.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Law may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Laws</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},phalanx:{a:'<p>The summoned avatars no longer march forward, but will wield bows and attack enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage. These bowmen follow you as you move for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>The Bowmen can only be summoned once every <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The summoned avatars charge the target and perform a shield bash, dealing an additional <span class="d3-color-green">180%</span> weapon damage to enemies at that location.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon warhorses that deal <span class="d3-color-green">490%</span> weapon damage and have a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance to Stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The avatars no longer walk forward, but stand at the summoned location, blocking all enemies from moving through.</p><p>The Avatars can only be summoned once every <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of sending the avatars out away from you, you summon <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Avatars of the Order to protect you and fight by your side for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds. Each Avatar will attack for <span class="d3-color-green">560%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The Avatars can only be summoned once every <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1729162028,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1729162028\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Summon powerful avatars who charge forward to the targeted destination. Enemies caught in the charge path take <span class="d3-color-green">490%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},provoke:{a:'<p>For each enemy successfully taunted, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">1073</span> additional Life on Hit for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.  </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Provoke no longer taunts, but instead causes enemies to flee in Fear for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Taunted enemies have their attack speed reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> and movement speed Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>For <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after casting Provoke, any damage you deal will also deal <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> increased Block Chance for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after casting Provoke.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3052489254,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3052489254\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Taunt all nearby enemies and instantly generate an additional <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath for every enemy taunted. Taunted enemies will focus their attention on you for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},punish:{a:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you deal <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> weapon damage as Holy to the attacker.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased Attack Speed for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">12874</span> increased Life regeneration for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you explode with fury dealing <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> weapon damage as Fire to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased Critical Hit Chance for your next attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:2997083095,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2997083095\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Strike your enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">335%</span> weapon damage and gain Hardened Senses, increasing your Block Chance by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shieldbash:{a:'<p>Increases the weapon damage of Shield bash to <span class="d3-color-green">875%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The shield shatters into other smaller fragments, hitting more enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">740%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">335%</span> of your shield Block Chance as damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Additional shields erupt from you in a cross formation. Enemies hit by any of the additional shields take <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your shield Block Chance as damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Shield Bash will now deal <span class="d3-color-green">1320%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> shield Block Chance as damage. The range is reduced to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The targeted monster is stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds. All other monsters hit are knocked back.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"hol"},icon:1249306807,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1249306807\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Charge at your enemy, bashing him and all nearby foes. Deals <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> of your shield Block Chance as Holy damage.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shieldglare:{a:'<p>Blinded enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> more damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies caught in the glare have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to be charmed and fight for you for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies with health lower than <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to explode when Blinded, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> Wrath for each enemy Blinded.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by the glare are Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:1440729579,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1440729579\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds</p><p>Light erupts from your shield, Blinding all enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards in front of you for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},slash:{a:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> increased Attack Speed for every enemy hit for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The slash becomes pure lightning and has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Slash gains <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> increased Critical Hit Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Carve a larger area in front of you, increasing the number of enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased armor for each enemy hit. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"fir",x:"fir"},icon:3666483739,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3666483739\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Ignite the air in front of you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">230%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},smite:{a:'<p>The chains bind those they hit, causing them to share one another\'s fate. Enemies who share fate will be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds if they move <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards away from each other.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit by the chains have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to be Immobilized in place for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The holy chains explode dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Holy to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">6437</span> increased Life regeneration for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds for every enemy hit by the chains. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase the number of additional enemies hit to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:622736444,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/622736444\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Smite enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards away with holy chains that deal <span class="d3-color-green">175%</span> weapon damage as Holy. The chains break off and strike up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> additional enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},steedcharge:{a:'<p>The war horse deals <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> of your Thorns every second to enemies through which you ride.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While riding the war horse, you recover <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of your maximum Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The war horse is engulfed in righteous fire, scorching all who cross its path for <span class="d3-color-green">550%</span> weapon damage per second as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Bind <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> monsters near you with chains and drag them as you ride, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage as Holy every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:1510491007,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1510491007\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> seconds</p><p>Mount a celestial war horse that allows you to ride through enemies unhindered for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sweepattack:{a:'<p>Enemies caught in the sweep are pulled toward you.</p><p>Sweep Attack\'s damage turns into Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit by the attack will catch on fire for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Heal for <span class="d3-color-green">5364</span> Life for each enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies hit by the sweep attack have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to be tripped and Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Sweep Attack increases your Armor by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:2186888616,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2186888616\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Wrath</p><p>Sweep a mystical flail through enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards before you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">480%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Weapon</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.crusader={blunt:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4041733339\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of Justice and Blessed Hammer by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Let your hammer educate the heathens in the error of their ways.</div> </div>',divinefortress:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1275320813\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your Armor is increased by a percent equal to your shield\'s Block Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"His shield whirled around him, faster than the eye could follow, creating an impenetrable barrier against his foes."—The Tale of Joryn</div> </div>',fanaticism:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4037170909\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the attack speed of Punish, Slash, Smite and Justice by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"My words are not new. The ancients embraced the Light completely, and it made them mightier than we can even imagine."—Akarat</div> </div>',fervor:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2531171338\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While wielding a <span class="d3-color-green">one-handed weapon</span>, your attack speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> and all cooldowns are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"As the wicked fall at your feet, you shall know the power of the crusade."—Sir Gyrfalcon the Swift</div> </div>',finery:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3553083011\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1.5%</span> Strength for every gem socketed into your gear.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">As you meditate upon those stones that contain the Light, you will find the Light within yourself.</div> </div>',heavenlystrength:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2960727425\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You can wield a <span class="d3-color-green">two-handed weapon</span> in your main hand while bearing a shield in your off hand.</p><p>Your damage dealt is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"You must quiet both mind and body in order to feel the Light.  Only then shall it unleash your hidden strength."—Cleric Akkhan</div> </div>',holdyourground:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3215582651\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You can no longer Dodge, but your Block Chance is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I shall not be moved. Your blows cannot touch me."—Harrel the Unbreakable</div> </div>',holycause:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2633328419\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The amount of damage dealt by your weapon is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p><p>Whenever you deal Holy damage, you heal up to <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your total Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Unleash your might upon the wicked that they may be cleansed."—Melmoth, the Wanderer of the Wastes</div> </div>',indestructible:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1099393495\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you receive fatal damage, you instead become immune to damage, gain <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> increased damage and gain <span class="d3-color-green">107284</span> Life per Kill for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"As my life drained away, I could no longer feel the blows raining down upon me."—Anajinn</div> </div>',insurmountable:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3955299278\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Blocking an attack generates <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Wrath.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Tenacity is measured by one\'s endurance against overwhelming odds.</div> </div>',ironmaiden:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2503653692\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your Thorns is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Woe to those who would approach a true crusader while carrying anger in their hearts, for soon, they shall be no more.</div> </div>',longarmofthelaw:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/510878592\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the duration of the Active effect of all Laws by <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The Light sustains the law, for without it, the law is naught but empty words"—Cleric Akkhan</div> </div>',lordcommander:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3252339261\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The cooldown of Steed Charge is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> and Bombardment by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span>.</p><p>Damage dealt by Phalanx is increased <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"You will follow, or you will fall."—Kassar</div> </div>',renewal:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3449330660\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Whenever you successfully block, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">16093</span> Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I say unto you, let not the foul darkness engulf the Light within you. For whosoever hears these words and knows them to be true shall be reborn."—Akarat </div> </div>',righteousness:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1833271637\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your primary skills generate an additional <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Wrath.</p><p>Increase maximum Wrath by <span class="d3-color-green">30</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The deeper your belief, the greater your power.</div> </div>',toweringshield:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2754902014\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of Punish, Shield Bash and Blessed Shield by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p><p>Reduce the cooldown of Shield Glare by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>70</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">A crusader\'s shield is one with his body.</div> </div>',vigilant:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4057131540\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase Life regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">2682</span>.</p><p>Reduce all non-Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"May Akarat protect me and grant me the faith to allow the Light to heal my soul."—The Crusader\'s Oath</div> </div>',wrathful:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3031537987\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Each point of Wrath spent heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">1341</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"One clad in the Light absorbs the anger of her foes and then turns it against them."—Crusader saying</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.demonhunter={bolas:{a:'<p>Increase the explosion radius to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Shoot <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> bolas that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Cold. The bolas no longer explode for area damage to nearby enemies.</p><p>Enemies hit have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to be <span class="d3-color-green">Frozen</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When the bola explodes, you have a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance to gain <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Discipline.</p><p>Bolas\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Augment the bola to deal <span class="d3-color-green">216%</span> weapon damage as Fire to the enemy and <span class="d3-color-green">148%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards, but increases the explosion delay to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"lit",d:"lit",e:"fir",x:"fir"},icon:1573036684,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1573036684\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot out an explosive bola that wraps itself around the enemy. After <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second, the bola explodes dealing <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to the enemy and an additional <span class="d3-color-green">110%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},caltrops:{a:'<p>Enemies in the area also take <span class="d3-color-green">270%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the slowing amount to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When the trap is sprung, all enemies in the area are immobilized for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cost of Caltrops to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Become empowered while standing in the area of effect, gaining an additional <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> Critical Hit Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:810901144,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/810901144\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Discipline</p><p>Lay a trap of caltrops on the ground that activates when an enemy approaches. Once sprung, the caltrops Slow the movement of enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>. This trap lasts <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},chakram:{a:'<p>A second Chakram mirrors the first. Each Chakram deals <span class="d3-color-green">220%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The Chakram path turns into a loop, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to enemies along its path.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The Chakram follows a slow curve, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Cold to enemies along the path.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The Chakram spirals out from the targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies along the path.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Surround yourself with a cloud of spinning Chakrams, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage per second as Physical to nearby enemies. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1799143751,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1799143751\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a swirling Chakram that deals <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies along its path.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},clusterarrow:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of the explosion at the impact location to <span class="d3-color-green">850%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Instead of releasing grenades, release up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> rockets at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">600%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Launch a cluster through the air, dropping grenades in a straight line that each explode for <span class="d3-color-green">650%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Instead of releasing grenades, release up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> rockets at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> weapon damage as Cold. You gain <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> Life per enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by the grenades have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p><p>Cluster Arrow\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:324597533,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/324597533\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a cluster arrow that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">650%</span> weapon damage as Fire into a series of <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> additional grenades that each explode for <span class="d3-color-green">250%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},companion:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your spider throws webs at all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards of you and him, Slowing them by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a spider companion that attacks enemies in front of him for <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The spider\'s attacks Slow enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your boar charges to you, then taunts all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a boar companion that attacks enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The boar increases your and your party\'s Life regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">10728</span> and resistance to all elements by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your wolf howls, granting you and your allies within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a wolf companion that attacks enemies in front of him for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Instantly gain <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Hatred.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a bat companion that attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The bat grants you <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Hatred per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Instantly pick up all health globes and gold within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a pair of ferret companions that each attack for <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The ferrets collect gold for you, increase gold found on monsters by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>, and increase your movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:439848148,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/439848148\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your raven deals an additional <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> damage on its next attack.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a raven companion that pecks at enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},elementalarrow:{a:'<p>Shoot a frost arrow that hits an enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> weapon damage as Cold then splits into up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> additional frost arrows. Enemies hit are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Shoot a ball of lightning that electrocutes enemies along its path for <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Shoot a fiery arrow that hits an enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire and explodes, immolating the ground for <span class="d3-color-green">315%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Shoot a shadow tentacle that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies along its path and returns <span class="d3-color-green">0.4%</span> of your maximum Life for each enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Shoot an electrified bolt for <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Lightning that Stuns enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second on a Critical Hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:184977554,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/184977554\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot a fire arrow that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies it passes through.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},entanglingshot:{a:'<p>Increase the Slow duration to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p><p>Entangling Shot\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Entangle and Slow up to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> enemies with each shot.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Entangled enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p><p>Entangling Shot\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase the Slow amount to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"lit",d:"fir",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1589427902,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1589427902\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Imbue an arrow with shadow energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage to the primary enemy and entangles up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> enemies, slowing their movement by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>When Entangling Shot hits an enemy, the Slow effect on all entangled enemies is refreshed.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},evasivefire:{a:'<p>Instead of backflipping, your Armor is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the damage of side bolts to <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Whenever a backflip is triggered, leave a bomb behind that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Physical in a <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yard radius after <span class="d3-color-green">0.6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the backflip distance to <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p><p>Evasive Fire\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of backflipping, increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p><p>Evasive Fire\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2594005641,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2594005641\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot a spread of bolts that hits the primary enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage and two additional enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage.</p><p>If an enemy is in front of you at close range, you will backflip away <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> yards.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fanofknives:{a:'<p>Remove the cooldown but add a <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Hatred cost.</p><p>Fan of Knives\' damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Also throw long-range knives that deal <span class="d3-color-green">620%</span> weapon damage to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> additional enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies hit are Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Fan of Knives\' damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds and increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1600%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> additional armor for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p><p>Fan of Knives\' damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:1221625994,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1221625994\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds</p><p>Throw knives out in a spiral around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">620%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards. Your knives will also Slow the movement of enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},grenade:{a:'<p>Throw a grenade that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Cold and leaves a cloud that deals an additional <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to enemies who stand in the area and <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> them.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Throw cluster grenades that deal <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage as Fire over a <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> yard radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Throw out <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> grenades that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire each.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Hurl a Lightning grenade that has a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to Stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"fir",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:1383355833,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1383355833\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Throw a grenade that bounces and explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},hungeringarrow:{a:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p><p>Hungering Arrow\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',b:'<p>If the arrow successfully pierces the first enemy, the arrow splits into <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> arrows.</p><p>Hungering Arrow\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each consecutive pierce increases the damage of the arrow by <span class="d3-color-green">70%</span>.</p><p>Hungering Arrow\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the chance for the arrow to pierce to <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Critical Hits cause a burst of bone to explode from the enemy, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1893827298,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1893827298\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a magically imbued arrow that seeks out enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage and has a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to pierce through them.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},impale:{a:'<p>The knife <span class="d3-color-green">pierces</span> through all enemies in a straight line for Cold damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The impact causes Knockback and has a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to Stun for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The enemy also burns for <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The knife ricochets to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> additional nearby enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards of each other.</p><p>Impale\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Critical Hits deal <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> additional damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2594944828,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2594944828\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Hatred</p><p>Throw a knife that impales an enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},markedfordeath:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of damage dealt to the marked enemy is also divided evenly among all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When the enemy is killed, the mark spreads to the closest <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards. This effect can chain repeatedly.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Mark an area on the ground of <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yard radius for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds. Enemies in the area take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> additional damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Attacks you make against the marked enemy generate <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Attackers heal for up to <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> of their maximum Life when damaging the marked enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:746746961,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/746746961\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Discipline</p><p>Mark an enemy. The marked enemy takes <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> additional damage for the next <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},multishot:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of Multishot to <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> and have <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased chance to be Critically Hit for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Every time you fire, launch <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> rockets at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the Hatred cost to <span class="d3-color-green">18</span>.</p><p>Multishot\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Knockback the first <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:303982585,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/303982585\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a massive volley of arrows dealing <span class="d3-color-green">360%</span> weapon damage to all enemies in the area.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},preparation:{a:'<p>Restore <span class="d3-color-green">75</span> Hatred.</p><p>Preparation has a <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Permanently increase maximum Discipline by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> Discipline over <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds instead of restoring it immediately.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> Life when using Preparation.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',e:'<p>There is a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance that Preparation\'s cooldown will not be triggered.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3714052661,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3714052661\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> seconds</p><p>Instantly restore <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},rainofvengeance:{a:'<p>Fire a massive volley of arrows at a large area. Arrows fall from the sky dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2800%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to all enemies in the area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Launch a volley of guided arrows that rain down on enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3500%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a Shadow Beast that drops grenades from the sky dealing <span class="d3-color-green">5800%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Call a group of <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Shadow Beasts to plummet from the sky at a targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">3800%</span> total weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds and <span class="d3-color-green">Freezing</span> enemies hit for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon a wave of <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Shadow Beasts to tear across the ground, knocking back enemies and dealing <span class="d3-color-green">4600%</span> total weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:3422491597,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3422491597\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Fire a massive volley of arrows at a large area. Arrows fall from the sky dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1500%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to all enemies in the area.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},rapidfire:{a:'<p>Rapidly fire grenades that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">545%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within a <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yard radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Fire lightning arrows that have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to pierce through enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While channeling Rapid Fire, launch <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> homing rockets every second. Each rocket deals <span class="d3-color-green">145%</span> weapon damage as Physical to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the initial Hatred cost to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> and ignite your arrows, causing them to deal Fire damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by Rapid Fire are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Rapid Fire\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:890686438,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/890686438\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Hatred initially, and an additional <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Hatred while channeling</p><p>Rapidly fire for <span class="d3-color-green">685%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sentry:{a:'<p>Create a chain between you and the Sentry and between each Sentry that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage every second to each enemy it touches.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The turret now fires piercing bolts.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The turret will also fire homing rockets at random nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The turret <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> all nearby enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> yards, Slowing their movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The turret also creates a shield that reduces damage taken by allies by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3326150325,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3326150325\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Hatred</p><p>Summon a turret that fires at nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">280%</span> weapon damage. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p><p>You may have <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> turrets active at a time.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">You gain a charge every <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds and can have up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> charges stored at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shadowpower:{a:'<p>Slow the movement speed of enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> increased movement speed while Shadow Power is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Reduce damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> while Shadow Power is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cost to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Double the total amount of Life per Hit gained.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1595292131,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1595292131\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> Discipline</p><p>Draw in the power of the shadows, gaining <span class="d3-color-green">26821</span> Life per Hit for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>Life per Hit gained is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> of your Life per Kill.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},smokescreen:{a:'<p>Remove the Discipline cost but increase the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration to <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> Life while invisible.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cost to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> movement speed while invisible.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:498378287,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/498378287\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> Discipline<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds</p><p>Vanish behind a wall of smoke, becoming momentarily invisible for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},spiketrap:{a:'<p>Increases damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1930%</span> weapon damage.</p><p>When deployed, enemies within range are instantly immobilized for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase to <span class="d3-color-green">2020%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p><p>On detonation, the blast slows any targets hit for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase to <span class="d3-color-green">1900%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p><p>Hatred generators will now detonate traps.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Simultaneously lay <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> traps.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When triggered lightning chain hits up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p><p>Lightning will also arc from any triggered trap to any armed traps within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards.<br/>All enemies are hit for <span class="d3-color-green">6700%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:3714901347,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3714901347\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Hatred</p><p>Lay a trap that remains dormant until another Hatred spender is used to detonate the trap. When detonated, the trap and all other traps will explode in a chain reaction for <span class="d3-color-green">1160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards of each trap.</p><p>You can have a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Spike Traps active at one time.</p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},strafe:{a:'<p>Throw out bouncy grenades that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">460%</span> weapon damage as Fire to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Leave an icy trail in your wake that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds and <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',c:'<p>In addition to regular shots, shoot off homing rockets for <span class="d3-color-green">130%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Movement speed increased to <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of normal running speed while strafing.</p><p>Strafe\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Throw out knives rather than arrows that deal an extra <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> damage on Critical Hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2184421717,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2184421717\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot at random nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">675%</span> weapon damage while moving at <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> of normal movement speed.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},vault:{a:'<p>Leave a trail of fire in your wake that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Remove the Discipline cost but add an <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While Vaulting, shoot <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> arrows for <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> weapon damage at nearby enemies. These shots are guaranteed Critical Hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p>',d:'<p>After using Vault, your next Vault within <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds has its Discipline cost reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies you vault through are knocked away and Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1765480092,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1765480092\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Discipline</p><p>Tumble acrobatically <span class="d3-color-green">35</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},vengeance:{a:'<p>Instead of Homing Rockets, summon allies from the shadows that attack for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Cold and <span class="d3-color-green">Freeze</span> your enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Vengeance fills your heart, reducing all damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Instead of Homing Rockets, launch <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Grenades at random enemies outside melee range on every attack that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage each as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Instead of Homing Rockets, the side guns are powered up into slower-firing cannons that deal <span class="d3-color-green">225%</span> weapon damage and heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">3.0%</span> of maximum Life per enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Hatred per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1368351649,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1368351649\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">90</span> seconds</p><p>Turn into the physical embodiment of Vengeance for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-gold">Side Guns:</span> Gain <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> additional piercing shots for <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage each on every attack.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-gold">Homing Rockets:</span> Shoot <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> rockets at nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage each on every attack.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-gold">Vengeance:</span> Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> increased damage.</p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.demonhunter={ambush:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/608154598\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> additional damage to enemies above <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The art of surprise is difficult, but rewarding to master." —Mynton, Demon Hunter</div> </div>',archery:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3333952724\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain a bonus based on your weapon type:<br/>Bow: <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased damage<br/>Crossbow: <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> Critical Hit Damage<br/>Hand Crossbow: <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> Critical Hit Chance<br/>2nd Hand Crossbow: <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Hatred per Second</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Feel the weight of the crossbow in your hand. Now... the wind, the distance, the target\'s speed. Good. Now try it with blood in your eyes and a demon at your throat." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',awareness:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3727829327\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you receive fatal damage, you instead vanish for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds and regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of maximum Life.</p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Everything is a test. Study your surroundings well, and you will pass." —Josen, Master Hunter</div> </div>',ballistics:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2724217296\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase damage of rockets by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span>.</p><p>In addition, you have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to fire a homing rocket for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage when you attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"How should I know who first invented these devices? Just make sure the correct end is pointed at the enemy and they\'ll do the rest." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',bloodvengeance:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/671040338\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your maximum Hatred is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">25</span>. In addition, gain <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Hatred and <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Discipline when you are healed by a health globe.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"If it bleeds you can kill it. Kill this one slowly." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',brooding:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1860876243\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">3.0%</span> Life regeneration per second for every second you remain stationary, stacking up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times. This bonus is reset <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after you move.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Never forget where you came from.</div> </div>',culltheweak:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4214899055\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase damage against Slowed or Chilled enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I\'ll show you the same mercy you showed my helpless family." —Tyla Shrikewing</div> </div>',customengineering:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3309907294\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the duration of your Caltrops, Marked for Death, Spike Trap, and Sentry by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span>.</p><p>Increase the maximum number and charges of Sentries to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> and number of Spike Traps to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The self-loading mechanisms built into most hand crossbows and traps are delicate and difficult to maintain. Extensive practice is required to use them properly.</div> </div>',grenadier:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2447865967\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of grenades by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.<br/>Increase the explosion size of grenades by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p><p>Upon death, you drop a giant grenade that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">1000%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Do not construct these devices by candlelight, nor by firelight. Once armed, be no closer than ten paces upon the count of three." —Explicit instructions from Quang the Chemist</div> </div>',hotpursuit:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/929589357\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds when you hit an enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Don\'t make me chase you back to Hell, vermin. I know a quicker way to send you there." —Tyla Shrikewing</div> </div>',leech:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1324876423\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">18507</span> Life per Hit.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> of your Life per Kill.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"For a Demon Hunter, killing is life. Kill, grow strong, and survive." –Mynton, Demon Hunter\n</div> </div>',nightstalker:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/989292478\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your primary skills generate an additional <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"How did I learn to hate, to kill, to flay the flesh from the bones of my prey without pity? You taught me." —Tyla Shrikewing\'s final words to Naragh the Sin Eater</div> </div>',numbingtraps:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3392294912\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Enemies you Slow, Chill, or hit with Fan of Knives, Spike Trap, Caltrops, Grenades, and Sentry fire have their damage reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Demonic anatomy is strange and diverse. At times they defy sanity, but in other ways they are just as vulnerable as we are." —Meditations on the Enemy</div> </div>',perfectionist:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1477444155\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce the Discipline cost of all skills by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>. Increase your Armor and resistance to all damage types by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p><p>Discipline is used to fuel many of your tactical and defensive skills.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Once the trap is sprung you must not relent until every last enemy has fallen. To hesitate is to invite disaster.</div> </div>',sharpshooter:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4022948488\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span> Critical Hit Chance every second. This bonus is reset <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second after you successfully critically hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Every creature has a vulnerability. Find it, and put an arrow in it." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',singleout:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2280375200\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> Critical Hit Chance against enemies who are more than <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards away from any other enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Wield your focus like a weapon.</div> </div>',steadyaim:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2176454368\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>As long as there are no enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards, all damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Flee if you can, demon. I have a quiver full of friends who fly faster than you." —Tyla Shrikewing</div> </div>',tacticaladvantage:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/852610358\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Whenever you use Vault, Shadow Power, Smoke Screen, or backflip with Evasive Fire you gain <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Never start a fair fight.</div> </div>',thrillofthehunt:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1178023747\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Enemies hit by your Hatred spenders are Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The first three were dead before they hit the ground. The others weren\'t so lucky." —Captain Rumford</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.monk={blindingflash:{a:'<p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">29%</span> increased damage for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds after using Blinding Flash.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Each enemy you Blind restores <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Spirit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Blinded enemies are also slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the duration enemies are blinded to <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies that are Blinded deal <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> reduced damage for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after the Blind wears off.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:1869915185,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1869915185\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Create a flash of light that blinds all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. Elite enemies recover faster, but suffer a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance to miss with attacks.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},breathofheaven:{a:'<p>Breath of Heaven also sears enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">505%</span> weapon damage as Holy. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the healing power of Breath of Heaven to <span class="d3-color-green">139469 - 182383</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Breath of Heaven increases the damage of your attacks by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> additional Spirit from Spirit generating attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after using Breath of Heaven.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Allies healed by Breath of Heaven have their movement speed increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:184169342,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/184169342\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>A blast of divine energy heals you and all allies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">69735 - 91192</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},cripplingwave:{a:'<p>Increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">255%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Crippling Wave\'s third attack has its range increased to <span class="d3-color-green">17</span> yards and Freezes enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p><p>Crippling Wave\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies hit by Crippling Wave deal <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> less damage for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Each enemy hit generates <span class="d3-color-green">2.5</span> additional Spirit.</p><p>Crippling Wave\'s damage turns into Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by Crippling Wave take <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> additional damage from all attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"hol",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:4253953495,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4253953495\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Spirit per attack</p><p>Unleash a series of large sweeping attacks that deal <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage as Physical to all enemies in front of you.</p><p>Every third hit also dazes enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> yards, slowing their movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> and attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},cyclonestrike:{a:'<p>Blast enemies with an explosion that deals <span class="d3-color-green">454%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the distance enemies will be pulled towards you to <span class="d3-color-green">34</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Cyclone Strike heals you and all allies within <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">31036</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">17%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the Spirit cost of Cyclone Strike to <span class="d3-color-green">26</span> Spirit.</p><p>Cyclone Strike\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies are Frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds after being pulled in.</p><p>Cyclone Strike\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"lit",e:"col",x:"hol"},icon:2383150363,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2383150363\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit</p><p>Pull up to <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards towards you, followed by a furious blast of energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">261%</span> weapon damage as Holy. </p> <p class="special">Focus</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},dashingstrike:{a:'<p>The last enemy you dash through is obliterated with a barrage of strikes, taking an additional <span class="d3-color-green">975%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> increased movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after using Dashing Strike.</p><p>Dashing Strike\'s damage turns into Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> increased chance to Dodge for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after using Dashing Strike.</p><p>Dashing Strike\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increases maximum charges to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span>.</p><p>Dashing Strike\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased attack speed for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after using Dashing Strike.</p><p>Dashing Strike\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"hol",c:"col",d:"lit",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:2297806700,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2297806700\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Charge</p><p>Quickly dash up to <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> yards, striking enemies along the way for <span class="d3-color-green">370%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">You gain a charge every <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds and can have up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> charges stored at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Techniques</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},deadlyreach:{a:'<p>Every third hit also increases the damage of all your attacks by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increases chance to knock enemies up into the air to <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> and the second and third hits gain increased area of effect.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Every third hit randomly damages enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">215%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Each enemy hit with the third hit reduces the Spirit cost of your next Spirit Spender by <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span>.</p><p>Deadly Reach\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">260%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"lit",d:"col",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:4228438802,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4228438802\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Spirit per attack</p><p>Project lines of pure force over a short distance for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>Every third hit has a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to knock enemies up into the air.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},epiphany:{a:'<p>Infuse yourself with sand, reducing damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Imbue yourself with water, causing your abilities to heal yourself and allies within <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">16093</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increases the bonus Spirit regeneration from Epiphany to <span class="d3-color-green">45</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Engulf yourself in flames, causing your attacks to assault enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">353%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Charge yourself with Lightning, causing your next attack after moving <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards to Stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"hol",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"hol"},icon:4039032154,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4039032154\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds</p><p>Have an Epiphany, increasing your Spirit Regeneration per Second by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> and enabling your melee attacks to instantly dash to your target for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Focus</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},explodingpalm:{a:'<p>Exploding Palm arcs up to <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards to another target.</p><p>Exploding Palm\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Exploding Palm no longer causes the enemy to bleed, but if the enemy dies while affected by Exploding Palm, they explode for <span class="d3-color-green">6305%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies hit take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> additional damage for <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',d:'<p>If the enemy explodes after bleeding, gain <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Spirit for each enemy caught in the blast.</p><p>Exploding Palm\'s damage turns into Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of bleeding, the enemy will burn for <span class="d3-color-green">1875%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> seconds. If the enemy dies while burning, it explodes causing all nearby enemies to burn for <span class="d3-color-green">3260%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"hol",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:4217834320,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4217834320\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Spirit</p><p>Cause an enemy to Bleed for <span class="d3-color-green">1200%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> seconds. If the enemy dies while bleeding, it explodes and deals <span class="d3-color-green">2770%</span> weapon damage as Physical damage to all nearby enemies.</p> <p class="special">Techniques</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fistsofthunder:{a:'<p>Release an electric shockwave with every punch that hits all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> yards of your primary enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Lightning and causes knockback with every third hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Every third hit also releases arcs of holy power, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">240%</span> weapon damage as Holy to up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> additional enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Fists of Thunder applies Static Charge to enemies hit for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds. Each time an enemy with Static Charge gets hit by you, there is a chance that every other enemy with Static Charge within <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> yards takes <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase Spirit generated to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span>.</p><p>Fists of Thunder\'s damage turns into Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Every third hit Freezes enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Fists of Thunder\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"hol",c:"lit",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"lit"},icon:1599418324,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1599418324\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> Spirit per attack</p><p>Teleport to your target and unleash a series of extremely fast punches that deal <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p><p>Every third hit deals <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Lightning split between all enemies in front of you.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},innersanctuary:{a:'<p>Dash to the target location, granting a shield that absorbs up to <span class="d3-color-green">107284</span> damage for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to allies within <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> yards and then creating Inner Sanctuary.</p><p>Absorb amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">28%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Inner Sanctuary duration is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds and cannot be passed by enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Allies inside Inner Sanctuary are also immune to control impairing effects.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Allies inside Inner Sanctuary are healed for <span class="d3-color-green">35779</span> every second.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">7%</span> of your Life per Second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies inside Inner Sanctuary have their movement speed reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:2508502738,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2508502738\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds</p><p>Create a runic circle of protection on the ground for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds that reduces all damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">55%</span> for all allies inside.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lashingtailkick:{a:'<p>Release a torrent of fire that burns enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">755%</span> weapon damage as Fire and an additional <span class="d3-color-green">230%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Hurl a column of fire that burns through enemies, causing <span class="d3-color-green">755%</span> weapon damage as Fire to each enemy it strikes.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies are chilled at long range, Slowing them by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Lashing Tail Kick\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Unleash a large roundhouse kick that deals <span class="d3-color-green">825%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit are stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Lashing Tail Kick\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:257300654,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/257300654\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit</p><p>Unleash a deadly roundhouse kick that deals <span class="d3-color-green">755%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},mantraofconviction:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Increase the strength of Mantra of Conviction so that enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">12%</span> increased damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Enemies affected by Mantra of Conviction take <span class="d3-color-green">38%</span> weapon damage per second as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Conviction also slows the movement speed of enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Killing an enemy that is affected by Mantra of Conviction grants you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> increased movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Enemies affected by Mantra of Conviction deal <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> less damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:4267880982,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4267880982\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Damage bonus is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">16%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards of you take <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased damage.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Mantra may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Mantras</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},mantraofhealing:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Increase the Life regeneration granted by Mantra of Healing to <span class="d3-color-green">21457</span> Life per Second.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">7%</span> of your Life per Second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Healing also heals <span class="d3-color-green">3576</span> Life when hitting an enemy.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of your Life per Hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Healing also increases maximum Life by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Healing also regenerates <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Spirit per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Healing also reduces damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> when below <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:4051286657,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4051286657\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Shroud you and your allies with a mystical shield that absorbs up to <span class="d3-color-green">62064</span> damage for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. Absorb amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> You and your allies within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards gain <span class="d3-color-green">10728</span> increased Life regeneration. The heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">7%</span> of your Life per Second.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Mantra may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Mantras</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},mantraofretribution:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Increase the amount of damage inflicted by Mantra of Retribution to <span class="d3-color-green">202%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Retribution also increases attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> for you and your allies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Enemies damaged by Mantra of Retribution have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Retribution has a chance to restore <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Spirit when dealing damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Enemies damaged by Mantra of Retribution have a <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> chance to suffer a feedback blast, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">101%</span> weapon damage as Holy to itself and nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:2510088668,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2510088668\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Increase the amount of damage dealt to <span class="d3-color-green">202%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> You and your allies within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards deal <span class="d3-color-green">101%</span> of your weapon damage as Holy to attackers when blocking, dodging or getting hit.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Mantra may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Mantras</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},mantraofsalvation:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Salvation also increases Dodge Chance by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Increases the resistance to all elements bonus to <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Salvation also increases Armor by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Salvation also increases movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Mantra of Salvation also protects you and your allies when reduced below <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> Life, granting a shield that reduces damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Each target may be protected by this effect once every <span class="d3-color-green">90</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1620214495,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1620214495\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> You and nearby allies gain an additional <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> increased resistance to all elements for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> You and your allies within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards gain <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> increased resistance to all elements.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Mantra may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Mantras</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},mystically:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your mystic ally splits into <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> allies that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">480%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> A mystic ally fights by your side that increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your mystic ally performs <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> wave attacks in quick succession, each dealing <span class="d3-color-green">625%</span> weapon damage as Cold and Freezing enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> A mystic ally fights by your side that infuses your attacks to Slow enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your mystic ally turns into a boulder for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds. The boulder deals <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage as Physical every second and rolls toward nearby enemies, knocking them up.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> A mystic ally fights by your side that increases your Life by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> You gain <span class="d3-color-green">100</span> Spirit.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> A mystic ally fights by your side that increases your Spirit Regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">4</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your mystic ally sacrifices itself to heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your maximum Life. The cooldown on Mystic Ally is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> A mystic ally fights by your side that increases your Life per Second by <span class="d3-color-green">10728</span>. The heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">7%</span> of your Life per Second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:4013763271,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4013763271\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your mystic ally has its damage increased by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> A mystic ally fights by your side. The ally deals <span class="d3-color-green">130%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical per swing. When the ally dies, it is reborn after <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Focus</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},serenity:{a:'<p>When activated, Serenity heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">93874 - 120695</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',b:'<p>While under the effects of Serenity, your movement is unhindered.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the duration of Serenity to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Protect allies within <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> yards with a shield that removes control impairing effects and redirects up to <span class="d3-color-green">120158</span> damage to you for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Shield amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',e:'<p>While under the effects of Serenity, enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards take <span class="d3-color-green">438%</span> weapon damage as Physical every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"phy",x:"hol"},icon:4264690927,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4264690927\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> seconds</p><p>You are enveloped in a protective shield that absorbs all incoming damage for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds and grants immunity to all control impairing effects.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sevensidedstrike:{a:'<p>Teleport to the enemy and increase damage dealt to <span class="d3-color-green">8285%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> strikes.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Seven-Sided Strike causes enemies to burn for <span class="d3-color-green">630%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Removes the Spirit cost and enemies hit by Seven-Sided Strike are Frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Each strike explodes, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">877%</span> weapon damage as Holy in a <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> yard radius around the enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:2868080664,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2868080664\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Spirit<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Dash rapidly between nearby enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">5677%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> strikes.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Focus</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sweepingwind:{a:'<p>Intensify the vortex, increasing the damage per stack to <span class="d3-color-green">145%</span> weapon damage. This increases the damage with <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> stacks to <span class="d3-color-green">435%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the radius of the vortex to <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards.</p><p>Sweeping Wind\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While your vortex is at <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> or more stacks, Critical Hits have a chance to spawn a lightning tornado that periodically electrocutes nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">95%</span> weapon damage as Lightning. Each spawned lightning tornado lasts <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Sweeping Wind\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',d:'<p>As long as your vortex is at <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> or more stacks, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Spirit per second.</p><p>Sweeping Wind\'s damage turns into Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',e:'<p>While your vortex is at <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> or more stacks, enemies damaged by Sweeping Wind for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> consecutive seconds are Frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Enemies cannot be frozen by Sweeping Wind more than once every <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Sweeping Wind\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:3804611664,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3804611664\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">75</span> Spirit</p><p>Surround yourself in a vortex that continuously deals <span class="d3-color-green">105%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards. The vortex lasts <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds and is refreshed each time you strike an enemy with a melee attack. Landing a Critical Hit has a chance to increase the vortex effect up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> stacks for a total of <span class="d3-color-green">315%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Techniques</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},tempestrush:{a:'<p>Enemies hit are knocked back and deal <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> reduced damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p><p>Tempest Rush\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increases your movement speed while using Tempest Rush by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards take an additional <span class="d3-color-green">135%</span> weapon damage as Lightning every second.</p><p>Tempest Rush\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the Spirit cost of Tempest Rush to <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Spirit and increase its damage to <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',e:'<p>After you stop channeling Tempest Rush, you cause an icy blast to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards. The damage of the explosion increases by <span class="d3-color-green">90%</span> weapon damage as Cold while channeling.</p><p>Tempest Rush\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2463202280,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2463202280\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Spirit</p><p>Charge directly through your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">390%</span> weapon damage while running.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},waveoflight:{a:'<p>Wave of Light Stuns enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p><p>Wave of Light\'s damage turns into Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Release bursts of energy that deal <span class="d3-color-green">830%</span> weapon damage as Fire to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon an ancient pillar that deals <span class="d3-color-green">635%</span> weapon damage as Lightning, followed by <span class="d3-color-green">785%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to enemies who remain in the area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increases the damage of Wave of Light to <span class="d3-color-green">1045%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Wave of Light deals an additional <span class="d3-color-green">820%</span> weapon damage as Cold in a line.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"col",x:"hol"},icon:3340198908,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3340198908\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">75</span> Spirit</p><p>Focus a wave of light that crushes enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">835%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},wayofthehundredfists:{a:'<p>Perform a short dash with the first attack and enemies hit take an additional <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. Fists of Fury damage can stack multiple times on the same enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the number of hits in the second strike from <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> and increasing damage to <span class="d3-color-green">423%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Critical Hits increase your attack speed and movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. This effect can stack up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times.</p><p>Way of the Hundred Fists\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Each enemy hit with the third hit increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Every third hit also generates a wave of wind that deals <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Cold to enemies directly ahead of you.</p><p>Way of the Hundred Fists\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:1764077782,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1764077782\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Spirit per attack</p><p>Unleash a rapid series of punches that strike enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">190%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.monk={alacrity:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/691056746\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the attack speed of Spirit Generators by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The harmony of mind, body, and spirit brings many blessings. A monk who has become as one will move like a storm crashing into the mountains. Fast, hard, and without hesitation." — Patriarch Anisim</div> </div>',beaconofytar:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/314328592\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce all cooldowns by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">It is only through hardship that we come to know our limits, and only through knowing our limits that we learn to shatter them.</div> </div>',chantofresonance:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1499771024\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The Spirit costs of Mantra activation effects are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> and you gain <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Spirit every second when you have a Mantra learned.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The world continues on the noble path, each of us carrying another, all connected, ever onward.</div> </div>',combinationstrike:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3908604714\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Each different Spirit Generator you use increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Master Wughan was not merely the first to perfect the six techniques. His true accomplishment was in weaving them into a style all his own.</div> </div>',determination:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2385770725\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Each enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span>, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Where a lesser man despairs at the number of his foes, a monk of Ivgorod prays for more." —Master Wughan</div> </div>',exaltedsoul:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1742673788\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase maximum Spirit by <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> and increase Spirit Regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> per second.</p><p>Spirit fuels your defensive and offensive abilities.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Endeavor to be one with the hidden truth and you will soar beyond the sky." —Waykeeper Tzo Krin</div> </div>',fleetfooted:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1932836290\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Strength out of place is no strength at all.</div> </div>',harmony:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2290536697\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> of your single elemental resistances from items instead increases your resistance to all elements.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Ice hunters brave months of frozen darkness. Desert traders bear relentless, scorching sun. This world is ours to endure.</div> </div>',momentum:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1068645732\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Moving <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Always in motion, flowing like water.</div> </div>',mythicrhythm:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2640655164\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Every third hit from a Spirit Generator increases the damage of your next damaging Spirit Spender by <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The spirit is inconquerable, it folds in upon itself, it grows, always strengthening." — Patriarch Anisim</div> </div>',neardeathexperience:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1234942918\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When receiving fatal damage, you instead restore <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> Life and <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> Spirit and are immune to damage and control impairing effects for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"We do not see what has been done, we only see what remains to be done." —Mantra of the Monks of Ivgorod</div> </div>',relentlessassault:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2336331887\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> more damage to enemies that are Blind, Frozen or Stunned.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Vylnas refused to fall, despite his mortal wounds. The last of the Five Monks, he would not let his brothers\' sacrifice be in vain; his determination turned the tide of the war, eventually leading to the full withdrawal of Entsteig\'s forces from the field of battle." —Poldamyr\'s Chronicle of the War of Thorns</div> </div>',resolve:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2196494234\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Damage you deal reduces enemy damage by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"It is not our place to make demands of nature, nor to acquiesce to those who would. First we learn what is right, then we protect what is right." —Master Wughan</div> </div>',seizetheinitiative:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1194449484\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Dealing damage to enemies above <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> Life increases your attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The Monks of Ivgorod are trained to move like water — flowing freely into open spaces and crashing hard against their foes.</div> </div>',sixthsense:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1287759776\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce all non-Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The final test of the Serpent\'s Form takes place in "The Pit of 12 Vipers." The initiates are not told about the 13th.</div> </div>',theguardianspath:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1978951700\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While dual-wielding, you gain a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to dodge incoming attacks. While using a two-handed weapon, all Spirit generation is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"No weapon can overcome the weakness of an undisciplined mind. They can only serve as an extension of the self." —Waykeeper Tzo Krin </div> </div>',transcendence:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/232963121\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Every point of Spirit spent heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">429</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">0.4%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">A life unlived is no different from death.</div> </div>',unity:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1119381057\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Each ally affected by your Mantras increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span>, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>, and has <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I thought I was done for, trampled into the snow. Suddenly I felt her hand on my shoulder. The warmth returned to my bones, and together we repelled the beasts." —Legends of the North</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.necromancer={armyofthedead:{a:'<p>Skeletal hands raise from the ground damaging enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">14000%</span> weapon damage as Poison. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Raise a massive skeletal army to pummel all enemies in a line dealing <span class="d3-color-green">12000%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Skeletons will rise from the ground and attack random targets for <span class="d3-color-green">50000%</span> total weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The skeletal army knocks all affected enemies towards the center.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-red">20%</span> health</p><p>Raise a storm of the dead that surround you damaging enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">15500%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"psn",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1053303729,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1053303729\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>Raise a massive skeletal army to pummel the targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">12000%</span> weapon damage as Physical in a <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yard radius.</p> <p class="special">Reanimation</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bloodrush:{a:'<p>Heals for <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> of your maximum health for every enemy passed through.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Removes the health cost.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Provides an additional charge but doubles the health cost.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increases your armor by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds after casting.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Leaves a corpse at your original location when used.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3995040806,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3995040806\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost: </span><span class="d3-color-red">5%</span> Health<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds</p><p>Shed your mortal flesh and reappear up to <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> yards away.</p> <p class="special">Blood & Bone</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bonearmor:{a:'<p>Increases the damage dealt to <span class="d3-color-green">145%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> seconds</p><p>Your armor absorbs all incoming damage and grants immunity to all control impairing effects but only lasts for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies hit are also stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Bone Armor\'s damage is turned into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-red">20%</span> Health</p><p>Increases your Life per Second by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> per target hit. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Bone Armor also increases your movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> for each enemy hit.</p><p>Bone Armor\'s damage is turned into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:436563001,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/436563001\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds</p><p>Rip bones from nearby enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">125%</span> weapon damage as Physical, and create armor that reduces damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> per enemy hit up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> enemies. Lasts for <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> secs.</p> <p class="special">Blood & Bone</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bonespear:{a:'<p>Each enemy hit has their attack speed reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> and your attack speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds stacking up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> times.</p><p>Bone Spear\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Instead of piercing now detonates on the first enemy hit dealing <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Physical to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for each enemy Bone Spear passes through.</p><p>Bone Spear\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Bone Spear turns into Blood Spear. Damage is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">650%</span> weapon damage as Physical at the cost of <span class="d3-color-red">10%</span> Health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Launch razor sharp teeth that deal <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies in front of you.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:21355379,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/21355379\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Essence</p><p>Summon a piercing projectile that causes <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Physical to all enemies it passes through.</p> <p class="special">Secondary\n</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bonespikes:{a:'<p>Bone spikes stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Now unleashes a line of spikes that deals <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage as Physical. Damage is increased by up to <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> for those further away.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Instead strikes the target and up to two nearby enemies with large bone pillars for <span class="d3-color-green">225%</span> weapon damage per second as Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Leaves a frost patch that reduces the movement speed of enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> secs.</p><p>Bone Spikes\' damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit bleed for <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds and heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">0.5%</span> of your total life over the duration.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"psn",d:"col",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3256951079,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3256951079\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> Essence</p><p>Summon bone spikes from the ground dealing <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Physical per second.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bonespirit:{a:'<p>Bone Spirit will now charm the target for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds at the cost of <span class="d3-color-red">5%</span> health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards are feared for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds when Bone Spirit detonates. Damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increases the maximum number of charges to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Bone Spirit explodes dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1250%</span> weapon damage as Cold to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards on detonation.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for each enemy that Bone Spirit passes through while seeking its target. Damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"psn",c:"phy",d:"col",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2627645939,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2627645939\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Launch a Bone Spirit that will seek enemies. Deals <span class="d3-color-green">4000%</span> weapon damage as Physical on impact.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">You gain a charge every <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds and can store up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> charges. Recharge time is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second for each corpse you consume.</span></p> <p class="special">Blood & Bone</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},commandgolem:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active: </span>The Golem becomes a tornado of bone carrying all nearby enemies to the targeted location, stuns them for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds and deals <span class="d3-color-green">2000%</span> weapon damage as Physical over the duration.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active: </span>The Golem sacrifices itself healing you for <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> of your health and reconstructs at the targeted location. As the Golem reconstructs, veiny tendrils damage nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active: </span>The Golem consumes corpses at the targeted location increasing its damage by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> per corpse.</p><p>Command Golem\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active: </span>Command the Golem to the targeted location where it collapses into a pile of <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> corpses.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active: </span>Command the Golem to launch an icy blast at the targeted location, freezing enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds and increasing their chance to be critically struck by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p><p>Command Golem\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2588728824,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2588728824\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active: </span>Command the Golem to the targeted location where it collapses into a pile of <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> corpses.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Raise a Flesh Golem to fight for you. Flesh Golem deals <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> weapon damage as Physical per attack.</p> <p class="special">Reanimation</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},commandskeletons:{a:'<p>Reduces the active Essence cost to <span class="d3-color-green">25</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Skeletal minions will heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">0.5%</span> of your total health per hit while being commanded.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The target of your command is frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Command Skeletons\' damage is turned to Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Now commands your skeletons to explode, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">215%</span> weapon damage as Poison to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Commanded skeletons go into a frenzy, gaining <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> increased attack speed while they attack the target.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"col",d:"psn",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2515775757,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2515775757\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Essence</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Command your skeletal minions to attack the target and increase their damage against it by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Raise skeletons from the ground every <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds to a max of <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> skeletons. Skeletal minions deal <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> weapon damage as Physical per attack.</p> <p class="special">Reanimation</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},corpseexplosion:{a:'<p>Corpses now explode away from you, hitting all targets in a cone.</p><p>Corpse Explosion\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Corpses pull themselves towards the nearest enemy before exploding, but Corpse Explosion now costs <span class="d3-color-red">2%</span> life per corpse.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Now explodes up to 5 corpses close to you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">525%</span> weapon damage as Poison to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Explosion radius is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Freeze all enemies caught in the explosion for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Corpse Explosion\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"psn",b:"phy",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:732775937,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/732775937\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Target an area exploding up to 5 corpses within <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> yards dealing <span class="d3-color-green">350%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Corpses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},corpselance:{a:'<p>Corpse Lance has a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to ricochet to one additional target.</p><p>Corpse Lance\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies become brittle increasing their chance to be crit by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds each time they are hit with Corpse Lance.</p><p>Corpse Lance\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Spend <span class="d3-color-red">2%</span> of your total health to launch an additional lance from yourself towards the target that deals <span class="d3-color-green">525%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Stuns the target for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Each lance slows the target by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> and reduces its damage by <span class="d3-color-green">6%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds. Stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p><p>Corpse Lance\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"psn",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"psn",x:"phy"},icon:2627097571,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2627097571\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Target an enemy to summon projectiles from nearby corpses that cause <span class="d3-color-green">1750%</span> weapon damage as Physical to the target.</p> <p class="special">Corpses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},deathnova:{a:'<p>Now heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your health per target hit and reduces damage dealt to <span class="d3-color-green">225%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Spines radiate outward and deal <span class="d3-color-green">475%</span> weapon damage as Physical within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Spend <span class="d3-color-red">10%</span> health to unleash a Blood Nova that deals <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> weapon damage as Physical to all nearby enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Leave a lingering patch of blight on the ground slowing enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> and causing them to deal <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> less damage for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Each cast increases the radius of your next Nova by <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> yards up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"psn",e:"psn",x:"psn"},icon:2971329230,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2971329230\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Essence</p><p>Unleash a Nova that deals <span class="d3-color-green">350%</span> weapon damage as Poison to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Secondary\n</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},decrepify:{a:'<p>Increase the potency of the movement speed reduction to <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> and decaying to normal potency over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Gain a <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> movement speed increase for every enemy cursed, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> cooldown reduction for every enemy cursed, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Damage reduction increased to <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span>, but no longer reduces movement speed.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Cursed enemies have a <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds when hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1920515023,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1920515023\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Essence</p><p>A crippling curse that reduces the enemy units\' movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> and reduces damage of affected enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Curses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},devour:{a:'<p>Each corpse consumed also restores <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Additionally consumes your minions for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Essence per minion killed.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Reduces all essence costs by <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> for each corpse consumed for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Becomes an aura that consumes all corpses within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards to restore <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> Essence per corpse.</p><p>The range of this effect is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your gold pickup radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increases maximum life by <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds for each corpse devoured.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2652333865,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2652333865\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Consume corpses within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards to restore <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Essence per corpse.</p> <p class="special">Corpses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},frailty:{a:'<p>Triggers at <span class="d3-color-green">18%</span> life but costs <span class="d3-color-red">10%</span> of your life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Essence when a cursed enemy dies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Cursed enemies explode for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage on death.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Cursed enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage from your minions.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Becomes an aura that curses all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p><p>The range of this effect is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your gold pickup radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1307519951,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1307519951\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Essence</p><p>A crippling curse that kills enemies with less than <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> health.  Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Curses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},grimscythe:{a:'<p>Heal for <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your health per enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies below <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> health have a <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> chance to be decapitated and instantly killed.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each enemy hit increases your attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Max <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> stacks.</p><p>Grim Scythe\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Essence per enemy hit</p><p>Slash with two summoned Scythes in front of you dealing <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Physical and push enemies together.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by the scythe have a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance to be inflicted with a random curse.</p><p>Grim Scythe\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"psn",x:"phy"},icon:3729327123,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3729327123\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Essence per enemy hit</p><p>Slash with a summoned Scythe in front of you dealing <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},landofthedead:{a:'<p>Your skills do not cost essence while Land of the Dead is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies in the Land of the Dead are periodically frozen.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies in Land of the Dead suffer <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage as Poison each second, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">10000%</span> weapon damage total.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',d:'<p>You are healed for <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> of your maximum life whenever you kill an enemy while Land of the Dead is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Every <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> enemies killed extends the duration by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.  </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:674033559,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/674033559\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>All corpse skills can be used at will for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Reanimation</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},leech:{a:'<p>Each cursed enemy increases your life regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">751</span> per second, up to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies that die while cursed will spread the curse to a nearby unaffected target.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Whenever a cursed enemy dies, you are healed for <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> of your Life per Kill.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Now curses the ground, healing you for <span class="d3-color-green">1.0%</span> of your maximum life every second for each enemy in the cursed area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Whenever a cursed enemy dies your potion cooldown is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2836246901,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2836246901\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Essence</p><p>Curse the target area. Cursed enemies heal the attacker for <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> of their total health when they are struck. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Curses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},revive:{a:'<p>Revived minions degenerate back into a usable corpse at the end of their duration.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increases the damage of revived creatures by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> but each Revive now costs <span class="d3-color-red">3%</span> health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Damage taken is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> for each revived minion active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Revived minions deal an additional <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> damage but last <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds. Damage dealt is turned into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When you revive a corpse, enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards run in fear for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. Damage dealt is turned into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"col",e:"psn",x:"phy"},icon:1378821893,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1378821893\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Target an area reviving up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> corpses within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Corpses</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},simulacrum:{a:'<p>Your maximum essence is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> while your Simulacrum is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',b:'<p>While active, your curse skills now apply all three curses.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Life costs for skills are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> while Simulacrum is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Now also creates a Simulacrum of Bone, but the duration is reduced to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',e:'<p>If you would die with a Simulacrum active, instead the Simulacrum is destroyed and you are fully healed.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3866471510,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3866471510\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-red">25%</span> Health<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>Create a Simulacrum made of blood that will duplicate your Secondary skills for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Blood & Bone</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},siphonblood:{a:'<p>Enemies are also slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> while you siphon blood from them.</p><p>Siphon Blood\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Essence gained is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">19</span> while you are at full health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increases the amount of health restored to <span class="d3-color-green">6%</span> but no longer restores Essence.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> each time damage is dealt. Max <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> stacks.</p><p>Siphon Blood\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',e:'<p>You pull in all health globes within <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> yards while siphoning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"psn",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:679490773,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/679490773\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Essence each time damage is dealt</p><p>Siphon the blood from the targeted enemy dealing <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>Siphon Blood heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> of your total health every second while channeled.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},skeletalmage:{a:'<p>Risen mages leave a corpse behind when they die or expire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Consumes all Essence to summon a powerful minion. The minion\'s damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> for every point of Essence consumed.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Risen mages cost <span class="d3-color-red">10%</span> health to cast but last an additional <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Raise a contaminated mage that channels an aura of decay for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage as Poison for its duration.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Raise a Skeleton Archer that deals <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p><p>Skeleton Archers increase your attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds each time they deal damage. Max <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> stacks.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"psn",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:265393923,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/265393923\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Essence</p><p>Raise a skeleton from the ground to attack your foes dealing <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Physical over two attacks. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Secondary\n</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.necromancer={aberrantanimator:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/309390964\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your minions gain <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> of your Thorns.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">What comes up from the grave must bring enemies down.</div> </div>',bloodforblood:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2184073905\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Picking up a health globe removes the health cost of the next Blood spell. This effect can stack up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">In life or death, blood holds considerable power.</div> </div>',bloodispower:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1161431971\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>After cumulatively losing <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your maximum Life, all ability cooldowns are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>. This effect cannot reduce an ability\'s cooldown more than once for each time that ability is used.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Priests of Rathma may die as others do, but their lives are never wasted.</div> </div>',boneprison:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4284625449\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Bone Spear, Bone Spikes, and Bone Spirit have a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance to trap enemies in a Bone Prison for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">What is flesh but a prison for bones?</div> </div>',commanderoftherisendead:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/614678564\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The Essence cost of Command Skeletons and the cooldown of Command Golem are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">One does not become a Priest of Rathma to lead the living.</div> </div>',darkreaping:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2594223920\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While using a scythe, gain <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> Essence and Life per kill.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">All apprentices train to use scythes, though they may come to favor other weapons later.</div> </div>',drawlife:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/243513400\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increases your Life regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> for each enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Our enemies must die, and we must stay alive. Altogether, we uphold the Balance." —Deathspeaker Jurdann</div> </div>',eternaltorment:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3436008702\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your curses cost <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> less Essence and last forever.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">It is said that being cursed is the most painful way to die.</div> </div>',extendedservitude:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1487390646\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the duration of your Skeletal Mage and Revive minions by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">A good minion should stay around for a while.</div> </div>',finalservice:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/421604773\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you take lethal damage, you are sustained preventing all damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds. In addition, you consume minions to heal for <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> of your Life per minion. This effect cannot occur more than once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Our minions serve the Balance by serving us." —Deathspeaker Rahad</div> </div>',fueledbydeath:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1345334176\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Consuming a corpse increases your movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. This effect can stack up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Few have dared to master the dark arts, but then, there are few like us." —Master Necromancer Ordan</div> </div>',grislytribute:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2390026691\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You are healed for <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> of your Life on Hit when one of your minions hits an enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Those who are fearful of the dead have not spent much time around them. I find them to be quite dependable." —Master Necromancer Mehtan</div> </div>',lifefromdeath:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3729622148\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Consuming a corpse has a chance to spawn a health globe.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Death finds a way.</div> </div>',overwhelmingessence:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3263208199\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase your maximum Essence by <span class="d3-color-green">40</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Essence is the spark that illuminates all living things.</div> </div>',rathmasshield:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1925756691\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You cannot lose Life for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after using Land of the Dead, Army of the Dead, or Simulacrum.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>70</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Let the wisdom of Rathma protect us from those that would do us harm." —The Books of Kalan</div> </div>',rigormortis:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2143552811\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Poison abilities also slow enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> and reduce their attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The point is not to perform the spell to meet expectations, but to defy them." —Deathspeaker Mykan</div> </div>',serration:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2904196257\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Bone Spikes, Bone Spear, and Bone Spirit deal <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> increased damage for every <span class="d3-color-green">1.5 </span> yards from you, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Bones are sharp, but our wits are sharper." —Master Necromancer Ordan</div> </div>',spreadingmalediction:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2145676656\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Receive a <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> damage bonus for each enemy afflicted by one of your curses.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The more effective the curse, the better it is to share it.</div> </div>',standalone:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1501311571\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase armor by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span>, reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> for each active minion.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Solitude is the one constant for those who have chosen our path." —Master Necromancer Jostan</div> </div>',swiftharvesting:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1311728370\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the attack speed of Bone Spikes, Siphon Blood, and Grim Scythe by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I did not offer my life to this service in order to watch you fight enemies slowly." —Master Necromancer Leger</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.witchdoctor={acidcloud:{a:'<p>Raise a corpse from the ground that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage as Fire to enemies in the area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the initial area of effect of Acid Cloud to <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The acid on the ground forms into a slime that irradiates nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">600%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Create pools of frost to deal <span class="d3-color-green">720%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Spit a cloud of acid that deals <span class="d3-color-green">333%</span> weapon damage as Poison, followed by <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"psn",c:"psn",d:"col",e:"psn",x:"psn"},icon:2280883641,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2280883641\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">175</span> Mana</p><p>Cause acid to rain down, dealing an initial <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Poison, followed by <span class="d3-color-green">360%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to enemies who remain in the area.</p> <p class="special">Decay</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bigbadvoodoo:{a:'<p>The Fetish increases the damage of all nearby allies by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration of the ritual to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The ritual heals all nearby allies for <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> of their maximum Life per second and reduces all damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The ritual restores <span class="d3-color-green">250</span> Mana per second while standing in the ritual area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies who die in the ritual area have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to resurrect as a Zombie Dog.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1757376672,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1757376672\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>Conjure a Fetish that begins a ritual dance that increases the attack speed and movement speed of all nearby allies by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Voodoo</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},corpsespiders:{a:'<p>Throw a jar with fire spiders that return <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Mana to you per hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Throw a jar with a spider queen that births spiderlings, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2625%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p><p>You may have one spider queen summoned at a time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Throw a jar with jumping spiders that leap up to <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards to reach their enemy and attack for a total of <span class="d3-color-green">645%</span> weapon damage as Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Throw a jar with widowmaker spiders deal a total of <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Throw a jar with paralyzing spiders that have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to Slow enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> with every attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"psn",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2157718487,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2157718487\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Throw a jar with <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> spiders that attack nearby enemies for a total of <span class="d3-color-green">576%</span> weapon damage as Physical before dying.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fetisharmy:{a:'<p>Each Fetish deals <span class="d3-color-green">680%</span> weapon damage as Cold to any nearby enemy as it is summoned.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase number of dagger-wielding Fetishes summoned by <span class="d3-color-green">3</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon an additional <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Fetish casters who breathe fire in a cone in front of them and deal <span class="d3-color-green">85%</span> of your weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Decrease the cooldown of Fetish Army to <span class="d3-color-green">90</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon an additional <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Hunter Fetishes that shoot blowdarts at enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">130%</span> of your weapon damage as Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"psn",x:"phy"},icon:2870927885,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2870927885\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>Summon an army of <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> dagger-wielding Fetishes to fight by your side for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds. The Fetishes attack for <span class="d3-color-green">180%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Voodoo</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},firebats:{a:'<p>Summon fewer but larger bats that travel a long distance and deal <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Rapidly summon two bats that each seek out a nearby enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Diseased bats fly towards the enemy and infect them. Damage is slow at first, but can increase over time to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">720%</span> weapon damage as Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Firebats has an initial Mana cost of <span class="d3-color-green">250</span> mana but no longer has a channeling cost.</p><p>Firebats\' damage type turns into Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Call forth a swirl of bats that damage nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">425%</span> weapon damage as Fire. The damage of the bats increases every second, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">850%</span> weapon damage after 3 seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"fir",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"fir",x:"fir"},icon:886583105,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/886583105\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">125</span> Mana</p><p>Call forth a swarm of fiery bats to burn enemies in front of you for <span class="d3-color-green">475%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},firebomb:{a:'<p>In addition to the base explosion, the skull creates a larger blast that deals an additional <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> weapon damage as Cold to all other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">28</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The skull can bounce up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The explosion creates a pool of fire that deals <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Create a column of flame that spews fire at the closest enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">880%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p><p>You may have up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Pyrogeists active at a time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Rather than exploding for area damage, each Firebomb can bounce to up to <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> additional enemies. Damage is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> per bounce.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"fir",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"fir",x:"fir"},icon:2376459543,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2376459543\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Lob an explosive skull that deals <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},gargantuan:{a:'<p>When the Gargantuan encounters an elite enemy or is near <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> enemies, it enrages for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds gaining:<br/> <span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> movement speed<br/> <span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> attack speed<br/> <span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> Physical damage</p><p>This effect cannot occur more than once every <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> seconds. Elite enemies include champions, rares, bosses, and other players.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The Gargantuan gains the Cleave ability, allowing its attacks to hit multiple enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">585%</span> of your weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The Gargantuan is surrounded by a poison cloud that deals <span class="d3-color-green">135%</span> weapon damage as Poison per second to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Summon a more powerful Gargantuan to fight for you for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds. The Gargantuan\'s fists burn with fire, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">575%</span> of your weapon damage as Fire and knocking enemies into the air.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The Gargantuan gains the ability to periodically slam enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> of your weapon damage as Fire and stunning them for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"psn",d:"fir",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:3792224409,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3792224409\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds</p><p>Summon a Gargantuan zombie to fight for you. The Gargantuan attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Voodoo</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},graspofthedead:{a:'<p>Increase the damage done to <span class="d3-color-green">1360%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Corpses also fall from the sky, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">420%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Removes the Mana cost and increases the amount enemies are Slowed to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p><p>Damage type is changed to Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cooldown of Grasp of the Dead to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p><p>Damage type is changed to Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies who die while in the area of Grasp of the Dead have a <span class="d3-color-green">70%</span> chance to summon a Zombie Dog.</p><p>Damage type is changed to Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"col",d:"psn",e:"psn",x:"phy"},icon:3737512178,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3737512178\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">150</span> Mana<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds</p><p>Ghoulish hands reach out from the ground, slowing enemy movement by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> and dealing <span class="d3-color-green">760%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},haunt:{a:'<p>The spirit returns <span class="d3-color-green">4291</span> Life per second.</p><p>Haunt\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>If there are no enemies left, the spirit will linger for up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds looking for new enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Haunted enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> more damage from your attacks.</p><p>Haunt\'s damage turns into Poison.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The spirit returns <span class="d3-color-green">13</span> Mana per second.</p><p>Haunt\'s damage turns into Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Release two spirits with every cast.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"psn",d:"phy",e:"col",x:"col"},icon:2198492913,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2198492913\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Mana</p><p>Haunt an enemy with a spirit, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">4000%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds. If the enemy dies, the spirit will haunt another nearby enemy.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">An enemy can only be affected by one Haunt at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},hex:{a:'<p>Summon a giant toad that pulls in enemies, briefly swallows them whole, then spits them back out with a layer of goo that deals <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds, Slows them, and increases their damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Transform into an angry chicken for up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds that can explode for <span class="d3-color-green">1350%</span> weapon damage as Poison to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Hexed enemies explode when killed, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The Fetish Shaman will periodically heal allies for <span class="d3-color-green">32185</span> Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Hexed enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> additional damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"psn",b:"psn",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"psn",x:"phy"},icon:1439096694,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1439096694\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Summon a Fetish Shaman for <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds that will hex groups of enemies into chickens. Hexed enemies are unable to perform offensive actions.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},horrify:{a:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> additional Armor for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds after casting Horrify.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the radius of Horrify to <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies are no longer Immobilized and will instead run in Fear for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">55</span> Mana for every horrified enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after casting Horrify.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3612919668,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3612919668\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds</p><p>Don a spectral mask that horrifies all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards, causing them to tremor in Fear and be Immobilized for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},locustswarm:{a:'<p>Engulf the enemy with burning locusts that deal <span class="d3-color-green">1480%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Locust Swarm has a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to jump to two additional enemies instead of one. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies affected deal <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> reduced damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Mana a second while the first enemy hit by a Locust Swarm cast is still affected by that swarm. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies killed while affected by Locust Swarm leave behind a cloud of locusts that deal <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to enemies who stand in the area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"psn",c:"phy",d:"col",e:"psn",x:"psn"},icon:1465459957,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1465459957\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">300</span> Mana</p><p>Unleash a plague of locusts that swarms an enemy, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1040%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p><p>The locusts will jump to additional nearby enemies.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},massconfusion:{a:'<p>All enemies in the area of Mass Confusion deal <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> less damage for <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> enemies who are not Confused become Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Amid the confusion, a giant spirit rampages through enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage per second as Physical to enemies it passes through.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cooldown of Mass Confusion to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies killed while Confused have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to spawn a Zombie Dog.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3808155897,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3808155897\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds</p><p>Incite paranoia in enemies, confusing them and causing some to be <span class="d3-color-green">Charmed</span> and fight for you for <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Terror</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},piranhas:{a:'<p>A giant bogadile emerges from the pool of water, <span class="d3-color-green">Stuns</span>, and bites a monster dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1100%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Turn the piranhas into zombie piranhas.  The piranhas will leap out from the pool savagely at nearby enemies</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The pool of piranhas becomes a tornado of piranhas that lasts <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.  Nearby enemies are periodically sucked into the tornado.</p><p>Increases the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Turn each cast into a wave of piranhas that crash forward dealing <span class="d3-color-green">475%</span> weapon damage and causing all enemies affected to take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Changes the damage dealt to <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds, chilling enemies for the entire duration.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"psn",c:"psn",d:"psn",e:"col",x:"psn"},icon:886161223,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/886161223\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">250</span> Mana<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds</p><p>Summons a pool of deadly piranhas that deals <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.  Affected enemies will also take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage.</p> <p class="special">Decay</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},plagueoftoads:{a:'<p>Mutate to fire bullfrogs that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">245%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Cause toads to rain from the sky that deal <span class="d3-color-green">182%</span> weapon damage as Poison to enemies in the area over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Mutate to frogs that pierce through enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">130%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> Mana every time a toad hits an enemy.</p><p>Plague of Toads\' damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Mutate to yellow toads that deal <span class="d3-color-green">190%</span> weapon damage as Poison and have a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance to Confuse affected enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"psn",c:"phy",d:"col",e:"psn",x:"psn"},icon:749261375,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/749261375\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Release a handful of toads that deal <span class="d3-color-green">190%</span> weapon damage as Poison to enemies they come in contact with.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},poisondart:{a:'<p>Ignite the dart, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">565%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Shoot <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Poison Darts that deal <span class="d3-color-green">110%</span> weapon damage as Poison each.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Shoot a Cold dart that will Slow the enemy by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Mana every time a Poison Dart hits an enemy. Converts the damage type to Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Transform your Poison Dart into a snake that has a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to Stun the enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"psn",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"psn",x:"psn"},icon:182799700,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/182799700\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Shoot a deadly Poison Dart that deals <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage as Poison and an additional <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sacrifice:{a:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> increased damage done for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after using Sacrifice.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Command all of your Zombie Dogs to charge the target at the same time, each dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1300%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Ichor erupts from the corpse of the Zombie Dog and Stuns enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">280</span> Mana for each Zombie Dog you sacrifice.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Each Zombie Dog you sacrifice has a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to resurrect as a new Zombie Dog.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3624441914,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3624441914\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Banish one of your active Zombie Dogs causing it to explode, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1090%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Terror</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},soulharvest:{a:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">32185</span> Life for every harvested enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased movement speed for each enemy harvested.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase your Armor by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> per harvested enemy and reduce their movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain mana and increase maximum Mana by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> for each enemy harvested.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Harvested enemies also take <span class="d3-color-green">640%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"psn",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2196086897,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2196086897\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds</p><p>Feed on the life force of enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards. Gain <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> Intelligence for <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds for each affected enemy. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p> <p class="special">Terror</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},spiritbarrage:{a:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">6437</span> Life each time Spirit Barrage hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>An additional <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> spirits seek out other enemies and deal <span class="d3-color-green">65%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a spectre that deals <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p><p>You can have a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Phantasms out at one time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Mana each time Spirit Barrage hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon a spectre that hovers over you, unleashing spirit bolts at nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">6000%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"col",e:"col",x:"col"},icon:1117784160,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1117784160\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">100</span> Mana</p><p>Bombard an enemy with <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> spirit bolts that deal a total of <span class="d3-color-green">600%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="special">Decay</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},spiritwalk:{a:'<p>Increase your movement speed by an additional <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> while in the spirit realm.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration of Spirit Walk to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When Spirit Walk ends, your physical body erupts for <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of your maximum Mana when you activate Spirit Walk.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of your maximum Life when you activate Spirit Walk.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3129485499,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3129485499\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds</p><p>Leave your physical body and enter the spirit realm for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds. While in the spirit realm, your movement is unhindered.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},summonzombiedogs:{a:'<p>Your Zombie Dogs burst into flames, burning nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> of your weapon damage as Fire every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Your Zombie Dogs absorb <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> of all damage done to you.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Your Zombie Dogs gain an infectious bite that deals <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> of your weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies who hit or are hit by your Zombie Dogs are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Your Zombie Dogs heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your Life On Hit with every attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"psn",d:"col",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:46288016,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/46288016\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> seconds</p><p>Summon <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Zombie Dogs from the depths to fight by your side. Each dog deals <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical per hit.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},wallofdeath:{a:'<p>Raise a circle of zombies from the ground that traps and attacks nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1250%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Summon a deadly ring for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds that poisons nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1200%</span> weapon damage as Poison over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a circle of spirits for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds that deals <span class="d3-color-green">1200%</span> weapon damage as Cold, Chills nearby enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>, and reduces their damage dealt by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the width of the wall to <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> yards. All enemies in front of you are knocked back behind the wall.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Raise a wall of flame <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> yards wide for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds that burns enemies who walk through, causing them to take <span class="d3-color-green">1100%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"psn",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:32183695,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/32183695\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds</p><p>Raise a wall of zombies <span class="d3-color-green">28</span> yards wide from the ground that blocks enemies and attacks them for <span class="d3-color-green">1200%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Decay</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},zombiecharger:{a:'<p>Summon zombie bears that stampede towards your enemy. Each bear deals <span class="d3-color-green">520%</span> weapon damage as Poison to enemies in the area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Zombie winter bears crawl out of the ground and run in all directions, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">280%</span> weapon damage as Cold to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a tower of zombies that falls over, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">880%</span> weapon damage as Physical to any enemies it hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',d:'<p>If the Zombie Charger kills any enemies, it will reanimate and charge nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">480%</span> weapon damage as Poison. This effect can repeat up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon an explosive Zombie Dog that streaks toward the enemy before exploding, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">680%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"psn",b:"col",c:"phy",d:"psn",e:"fir",x:"psn"},icon:1974566355,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1974566355\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">150</span> Mana</p><p>Call forth a reckless, suicidal zombie that deals <span class="d3-color-green">560%</span> weapon damage as Poison to all enemies in its path before decomposing.</p> <p class="special">Decay</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.witchdoctor={badmedicine:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4188953228\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you deal Poison damage to an enemy, its damage is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Their mastery of paralytic agents is astounding. The jungle, they say, provides ample demonstration of its wonders." —Abner Lockridge</div> </div>',bloodritual:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/687686877\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of Mana costs are paid with Life. In addition, you regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your maximum Life per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"To give of one\'s self... Is there any greater gift?" —Final words spoken at the Ritual of Blood</div> </div>',circleoflife:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2457736647\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When an enemy dies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards, there is a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance that a Zombie Dog will automatically emerge.</p><p>The range of this effect is increased by your gold pickup radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The heads hanging in the village had their eyes sewn shut with thick thread. Whatever wicked magic held the frightful hound-beasts together was considerably stronger." —Abner Lockridge</div> </div>',confidenceritual:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2423319440\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> additional damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Take your enemies into your confidence. Bring them close, so that they may share the fruits of your efforts.</div> </div>',creepingdeath:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2667474682\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your Haunt, Locust Swarm and the damage amplification from Piranhas last almost forever. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">There are some terrors that cannot be outrun. Bit by bit, second by second, they consume you.</div> </div>',fetishsycophants:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1895988520\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you hit enemies with your spells, you have up to a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance to summon a dagger-wielding Fetish to fight by your side for <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The denizens of the Unformed Land are mischievous and drawn to power, always seeking to intrude upon our world, but too fickle to stay for long.</div> </div>',fierceloyalty:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3265990692\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While you have a Gargantuan, Zombie Dog, or Fetish summoned, your movement speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p><p>This bonus is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> while a Gargantuan, Zombie Dog, or Fetish is not in combat.</p><p>Additionally, you may have <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> additional Zombie Dog summoned at one time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Establish dominance. They will obey.</div> </div>',graveinjustice:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2831706474\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your maximum Life and Mana and reduce the cooldown of all of your skills by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second when an enemy dies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p><p>The range is extended by items that increase your gold pickup radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Only a fool tries to cheat death. The wise offer a fair trade.</div> </div>',gruesomefeast:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2004785790\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you are healed by a health globe, gain <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> of your maximum Mana and <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> Intelligence for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds. The Intelligence bonus stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"We are all connected in life and in death. Partake of the spirits of the dead and flourish like the jungle that grows wild after the fire." —Shadewalker Zunimassa</div> </div>',junglefortitude:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1411119650\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce all damage taken by you and your pets by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">To be one with the jungle is to take what you need and endure what you must.</div> </div>',midnightfeast:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2772105166\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The damage of your Zombie Dogs and Gargantuan is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p><p>Additionally, you may have <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> additional Zombie Dog summoned at one time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">In the deepest hour of night, they emerge for the hunt.</div> </div>',piercetheveil:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/989292478\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>All of your damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>, but your Mana costs are increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The spirits take their toll. Best to be ready to pay." —Shadewalker Zunimassa</div> </div>',rushofessence:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1545737749\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Spirit spells return <span class="d3-color-green">100</span> Mana over <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p><p>Spirit spells are:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Haunt<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Horrify<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Mass Confusion<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Soul Harvest<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Spirit Barrage<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Spirit Walk</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">All spirits must move onward if they wish to return to their origins. There is no going back.</div> </div>',spiritualattunement:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/520015337\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Maximum Mana is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>. Regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> of your maximum Mana per second.</p><p>Mana fuels your offensive and defensive skills.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The pool is deep and still, cool and silent. Now a fountain, now a whirlpool. Drink and be renewed." —Runic carvings on the Shallow Stone</div> </div>',spiritvessel:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1523375412\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you receive fatal damage, you automatically enter the spirit realm for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds and heal to <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your maximum Life. </p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Everyone dies. Sometimes we must return to finish what we started.</div> </div>',swamplandattunement:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3976783465\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You and your pets gain <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> Physical, Poison, Fire, and Cold Resistance for every enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p><p>The range of this effect is increased by your gold pickup radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Know your enemies. Know their strength. Make it your own.</div> </div>',tribalrites:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2588768459\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce the cooldowns of the following skills by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Hex<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Gargantuan<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Fetish Army<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Summon Zombie Dogs<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Big Bad Voodoo<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Mass Confusion</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Befriend those who come from the Unformed Land, and they will befriend you." —Zuwadza of the Tribe of the Five Hills</div> </div>',visionquest:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3575003783\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you deal damage with Corpse Spiders, Firebomb, Plague of Toads, or Poison Dart, your Mana regeneration is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"You sense but do not see. Walk beside yourself in the Unformed Land. Walk until you find yourself again, or wander lost forever." —Chant of Ordeal</div> </div>',zombiehandler:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1366430649\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your Life, and that of your Zombie Dogs and Gargantuan are increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p><p>Additionally, you may have <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> additional Zombie Dog summoned at one time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The dead are willing minions. Death to them is not unknown, therefore need not be feared.</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.wizard={arcaneorb:{a:'<p>Increase the speed of the orb and its damage to <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage as Arcane, but reduce the area of effect to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Lob an electrified orb over enemies that zaps them for <span class="d3-color-green">349%</span> weapon damage as Lightning and increases the damage of the next Lightning spell you cast by <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> for every enemy hit up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">15</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Create <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Arcane Orbs that orbit you, exploding for <span class="d3-color-green">265%</span> weapon damage as Arcane when enemies get close. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Launch a burning orb that deals <span class="d3-color-green">221%</span> weapon damage as Fire. The orb leaves behind a wall of Fire that deals <span class="d3-color-green">734%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Create an orb of frozen death that shreds an area with ice bolts, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">950%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"lit",c:"arc",d:"fir",e:"col",x:"arc"},icon:2680277445,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2680277445\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Hurl an orb of pure energy that explodes on contact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">435%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},arcanetorrent:{a:'<p>You take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> less damage from attacks while channeling. Every second you channel increases this amount by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span>, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> damage reduction.</p><p>Arcane Torrent\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit by Arcane Torrent have a <span class="d3-color-green">12.5%</span> chance to fire a new missile at a nearby enemy dealing <span class="d3-color-green">582%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Lay Arcane mines that arm after <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds. These mines explode when an enemy approaches, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">825%</span> weapon damage as Arcane. Enemies caught in the explosion have their movement and attack speeds reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Each missile explodes into <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> piercing bolts of electricity that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Unleash a torrent of power beyond your control. You no longer direct where the projectiles go, but their damage is greatly increased to <span class="d3-color-green">1215%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p><p>Arcane Torrent damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">640%</span> weapon damage every second, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">2495%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"arc",c:"arc",d:"lit",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:1779828560,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1779828560\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Hurl a barrage of arcane projectiles that deal <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to all enemies near the impact location.</p><p>Arcane Torrent damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">305%</span> weapon damage every second, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">1010%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},archon:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of all Archon abilities by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Archon form can cast a <span class="d3-color-green">Slow Time</span> that follows you and your Arcane Blast and Arcane Strike abilities Freeze enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p><p>Archon abilities deal <span class="d3-color-green">Cold</span> damage instead of Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Archon form can cast <span class="d3-color-green">Teleport</span> with a <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Decrease the cooldown of Archon to <span class="d3-color-green">100</span> seconds.</p><p>Archon abilities deal <span class="d3-color-green">Lightning</span> damage instead of Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',e:'<p>An explosion erupts around you when you transform, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">3680%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p><p>Archon abilities deal <span class="d3-color-green">Fire</span> damage instead of Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"col",c:"arc",d:"lit",e:"fir",x:"arc"},icon:3123915539,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3123915539\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">120</span> seconds</p><p>Transform into a being of pure arcane energy for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds. While in Archon form, your normal abilities are replaced by powerful Archon abilities, your damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>, and your Armor and resistances are increased by <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span>.</p><p>Each enemy killed while in Archon form increases your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">6%</span> for the remaining duration of Archon.</p> <p class="special">Mastery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},blackhole:{a:'<p>Increases the Black Hole radius to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards and damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1290%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The Black Hole also absorbs enemy projectiles and objects from Elite monster affixes within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Conjure a Black Hole at the target location that draws enemies to it and deals <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p><p>After the Black Hole disappears, an explosion occurs that deals <span class="d3-color-green">725%</span> weapon damage as Fire to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies hit by Black Hole deal <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> reduced damage for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Each enemy hit by Black Hole grants you <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> increased damage for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Each enemy hit increases the damage of your Cold spells by <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p><p>Black Hole\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"arc",c:"fir",d:"arc",e:"col",x:"arc"},icon:3713685789,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3713685789\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Arcane Power<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds</p><p>Conjure a Black Hole at the target location that draws enemies to it and deals <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage as Arcane over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Mastery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},blizzard:{a:'<p>Increase the duration and damage of Blizzard to deal <span class="d3-color-green">1810%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the area of effect of Blizzard to a <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yard radius.</p><p>Blizzard\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies affected by Blizzard take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage from Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the casting cost of Blizzard to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Arcane Power.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies caught in the Blizzard have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to be Frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">2.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"fir",c:"lit",d:"col",e:"col",x:"col"},icon:4138616090,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4138616090\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Call down shards of ice that deal <span class="d3-color-green">1075%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to enemies in a <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yard radius. Multiple casts in the same area from the same caster do not stack.</p> <p class="special">Force</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},diamondskin:{a:'<p>Increases your movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> while Diamond Skin is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration of Diamond Skin to <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the maximum amount of damage absorbed to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> of your Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the Arcane Power cost of all skills by <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> while Diamond Skin is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When Diamond Skin fades, diamond shards explode in all directions dealing <span class="d3-color-green">863%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"arc",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:3225293865,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3225293865\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Transform your skin to diamond for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds, absorbing up to <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> of your Life in damage from incoming attacks.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},disintegrate:{a:'<p>Enemies hit by Disintegrate take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage from Arcane for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the width of the beam allowing it to hit more enemies.</p><p>Disintegrate\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The beam fractures into a short-ranged cone that deals <span class="d3-color-green">435%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p><p>Disintegrate damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">340%</span> weapon damage every second, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">1115%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',d:'<p>While channeling the beam you become charged with energy and discharge at nearby enemies dealing <span class="d3-color-green">115%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies killed by the beam have a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to explode causing <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"fir",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:1714727035,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1714727035\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Channel a beam of pure energy, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">390%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p><p>Disintegrate damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">250%</span> weapon damage every second, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">890%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},electrocute:{a:'<p>Create streaks of lightning that pierce through enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the maximum number of enemies that can be electrocuted to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Blast a cone of lightning that deals <span class="d3-color-green">310%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to all affected enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Arcane Power for each enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Critical Hits release <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> charged bolts in random directions, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">44%</span> weapon damage as Fire to any enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"lit",c:"lit",d:"lit",e:"fir",x:"lit"},icon:3898331671,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3898331671\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Lightning arcs from your fingertips, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">138%</span> weapon damage as Lightning. The lightning can jump, hitting up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> additional enemies.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},energyarmor:{a:'<p>Energy Armor also increases your resistance to all damage types <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Rather than decreasing your maximum Arcane Power, Energy Armor increases it by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Incoming attacks that would deal more than <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> of your maximum Life are reduced to deal <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> of your maximum Life instead.</p><p>The amount absorbed cannot exceed <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your maximum Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',d:'<p>You have a chance to gain <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Arcane Power when you are hit by a ranged or melee attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Energy Armor also increases your Critical Hit Chance by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"arc",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:1709064835,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1709064835\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Focus your energies, increasing your Armor by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> but decreasing your maximum Arcane Power by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span>. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Armor may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Conjuration</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},energytwister:{a:'<p>Enemies hit by Energy Twister take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage from Fire for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When two Energy Twisters collide, they merge into a tornado with increased area of effect that causes <span class="d3-color-green">3200%</span> weapon damage as Arcane over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each cast of Energy Twister grants you a Lightning Charge. You can store up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Lightning Charges at a time. Casting a Signature spell releases all Lightning Charges as a bolt of Lightning that deals <span class="d3-color-green">196%</span> weapon damage as Lightning per Lightning Charge.</p><p>Energy Twister\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p><p>The following skills are Signature spells:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Magic Missile<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Shock Pulse<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Spectral Blade<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Electrocute</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the casting cost of Energy Twister to <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Arcane Power.</p><p>Energy Twister\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Energy Twister no longer travels but spins in place, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">835%</span> weapon damage as Arcane over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to everything caught in it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"arc",c:"lit",d:"col",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:1154209487,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1154209487\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">35</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Unleash a twister of pure energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">1525%</span> weapon damage as Arcane over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to everything in its path.</p> <p class="special">Force</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},explosiveblast:{a:'<p>Immediately release the energy of Explosive Blast for <span class="d3-color-green">909%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Release an enormous Explosive Blast that deals <span class="d3-color-green">990%</span> weapon damage as Cold to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Reduce the cooldown of Explosive Blast to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Explosive Blast\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increases the damage of Explosive Blast to <span class="d3-color-green">1485%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of a single explosion, release a chain of <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> consecutive explosions, each dealing <span class="d3-color-green">520%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"lit",d:"arc",e:"fir",x:"arc"},icon:692400941,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/692400941\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Arcane Power<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds</p><p>Gather an infusion of energy around you that explodes after <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds for <span class="d3-color-green">945%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Mastery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},familiar:{a:'<p>Summon a fiery Familiar that grants you <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> increased damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The Familiar\'s projectiles explode on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">240%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The Familiar\'s projectiles have a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to Freeze the enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p>While the Familiar is active, you regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">4.5</span> Arcane Power every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon a protective Familiar. When you are below <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> Life the Familiar will absorb damage from <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> attack every <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"arc",c:"col",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:4193597309,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4193597309\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Summon a Familiar that attacks your enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">240%</span> weapon damage as Arcane. This companion cannot be targeted or damaged by enemies. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p> <p class="special">Conjuration</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},frostnova:{a:'<p>Enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">33%</span> more damage while frozen or chilled by Frost Nova.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',b:'<p>A frozen enemy that is killed has a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance of releasing another Frost Nova.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Frost Nova no longer freezes enemies, but instead leaves behind a mist of frost that deals <span class="d3-color-green">915%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">7.5</span> seconds and increase the Freeze duration to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain a <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> bonus to Critical Hit Chance for <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> seconds if Frost Nova hits <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> or more enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"col",c:"col",d:"col",e:"col",x:"col"},icon:3386826874,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3386826874\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> seconds</p><p>Blast nearby enemies with an explosion of ice and freeze them for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},hydra:{a:'<p>Summon a Frost Hydra that breathes a short range cone of frost, causing <span class="d3-color-green">255%</span> weapon damage as Cold to all enemies in the cone.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Summon a Lightning Hydra that electrocutes enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">255%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a Blazing Hydra that spits bolts of Fire that burn enemies near the point of impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. Burn damage can stack multiple times on the same enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Summon a Mammoth Hydra that breathes a river of flame at nearby enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> weapon damage per second as Fire to enemies caught on the burning ground.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon an Arcane Hydra that spits Arcane Orbs that explode on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">205%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to enemies near the explosion.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"arc",x:"fir"},icon:3239591952,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3239591952\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Summon a multi-headed Hydra for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds that attacks enemies with bolts of fire dealing <span class="d3-color-green">165%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Hydra may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Force</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},icearmor:{a:'<p>Melee attackers also take <span class="d3-color-green">189%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Lower the temperature of the air around you. Nearby enemies are chilled, slowing their movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',c:'<p>A whirling storm of ice builds around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage as Cold every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When you are struck by a melee attack, your Armor is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Melee attacks have a <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> chance to create a Frost Nova centered on the attacker, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"col",c:"col",d:"col",e:"col",x:"col"},icon:3362898666,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3362898666\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Surround yourself in a barrier of ice that reduces damage from melee attacks by <span class="d3-color-green">12%</span>. Melee attackers are either Chilled or Frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Armor may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Conjuration</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},magicmissile:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of Magic Missile to <span class="d3-color-green">325%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Fire <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> missiles that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The missile pierces through enemies and causes them to burn for <span class="d3-color-green">130%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Burn damage stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times and any Fire damage taken from your other spells refresh all stacks to their maximum duration.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Cast out a shard of ice that explodes on impact, causing enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">4.5</span> yards to take <span class="d3-color-green">175%</span> weapon damage as Cold and be Frozen for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p><p>Enemies cannot be Frozen by Glacial Spike more than once every <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Missiles track the nearest enemy. Missile damage is increased to <span class="d3-color-green">285%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"arc",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:3402782127,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3402782127\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Launch a missile of magic energy, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">230%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},magicweapon:{a:'<p>Attacks have a chance to burn enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Attacks have a chance to cause lightning to arc to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> nearby enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">61%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the damage bonus of Magic Weapon to <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies hit by your attacks restore up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Arcane Power.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When you perform an attack, gain a protective shield for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds that absorbs <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span> of your Life in damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:2800719875,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2800719875\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Imbue your weapon with magical energy, granting it <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> increased damage. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Weapon</span></p> <p class="special">Conjuration</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},meteor:{a:'<p>Greatly increases the size and increases the damage of the Meteor impact to <span class="d3-color-green">1648%</span> weapon damage as Fire and the molten fire to <span class="d3-color-green">625%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Adds a <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Unleash a volley of <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> small Meteors that each strike for <span class="d3-color-green">277%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a Comet that deals <span class="d3-color-green">740%</span> weapon damage as Cold and freezes chilled enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second upon impact.</p><p>The impact site is covered in an icy mist that deals <span class="d3-color-green">235%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Expend all remaining Arcane Power. Each point of extra Arcane Power spent increases the impact damage of Meteor by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Removes the delay before Meteor comes crashing down.</p><p>Meteor\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"fir",c:"col",d:"arc",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:1985710244,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1985710244\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Summon an immense Meteor that plummets from the sky, crashing into enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">740%</span> weapon damage as Fire. The ground it hits is scorched with molten fire that deals <span class="d3-color-green">235%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Force</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},mirrorimage:{a:'<p>Spells cast by your Mirror Images will deal <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of the damage of your own spells.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Summon <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Mirror Images that taunt nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second and each have <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the Life of your Mirror Images to <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> of your own.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the duration of your Mirror Images to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds and their Life to <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When a Mirror Image is destroyed, it explodes, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">309%</span> weapon damage as Arcane with a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to Stun for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"arc",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:1585093686,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1585093686\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Summon <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> illusionary duplicates of yourself that taunt nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second, last for <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> seconds and have <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your Life.</p><p>Spells cast by your Mirror Images will deal <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> of the damage of your own spells.</p> <p class="special">Mastery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},rayoffrost:{a:'<p>Enemies hit by Ray of Frost take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage from Cold for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Create a swirling storm around you that grows up to a <span class="d3-color-green">22</span> yard radius, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Cold to all enemies caught within it.</p><p>Ray of Frost damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">220%</span> weapon damage every second, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">740%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Ray of Frost has a <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> chance to Freeze enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second and increases the Slow amount to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce channeling cost to <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> Arcane Power.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies killed by Ray of Frost leave behind a patch of ice that deals <span class="d3-color-green">1625%</span> weapon damage as Cold to enemies moving through it over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"col",c:"col",d:"col",e:"col",x:"col"},icon:448906631,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/448906631\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Project a beam of frozen ice that blasts enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> yards of the first enemy hit for <span class="d3-color-green">430%</span> weapon damage as Cold and Slows their movement by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Ray of Frost damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">405%</span> weapon damage every second, up to a maximum total of <span class="d3-color-green">1240%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shockpulse:{a:'<p>Cast <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> bolts of fire that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">274%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Conjure a being of lightning that drifts forward, electrocuting nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">165%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Merge the bolts in a single giant orb that oscillates forward dealing <span class="d3-color-green">214%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to everything it hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Arcane Power for each enemy hit.</p><p>Shock Pulse\'s damage turns into Arcane.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Slain enemies explode, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">184%</span> weapon damage as Cold to every enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p><p>Shock Pulse\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"lit",d:"arc",e:"col",x:"lit"},icon:3881606583,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3881606583\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Release a medium range pulse of <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> unpredictable charges of electricity that deal <span class="d3-color-green">194%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},slowtime:{a:'<p>Enemies caught in the bubble of warped time take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> more damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies that enter or leave the Slow Time area are stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the potency of the movement speed reduction to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> and reduces the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies caught by Slow Time deal <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> less damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Time is sped up for any allies standing in the area, increasing their attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"arc",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:305262860,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/305262860\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Invoke a bubble of warped time and space at your target location up to <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards away for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds, reducing enemy attack speed by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> and movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>. This bubble also slows the speed of enemy projectiles by <span class="d3-color-green">90%</span>.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},spectralblade:{a:'<p>Each enemy hit increases the damage of your Fire spells by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span>, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>, for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Extend the reach of Spectral Blade to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards and increase its damage to <span class="d3-color-green">231%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Chilled enemies have a <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> chance to be Frozen and Frozen enemies have a <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased chance to be critically hit by Spectral Blade.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Arcane Power for each enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',e:'<p>With each cast, gain a protective shield for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds that absorbs <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span> of your Life in damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"col",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:1247273774,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1247273774\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.</span></p><p>Summon a spectral blade that strikes all enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards in front of you for <span class="d3-color-green">168%</span> weapon damage as Arcane.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},stormarmor:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of the shock to <span class="d3-color-green">315%</span> weapon damage as Lightning. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase your movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds when you are hit by melee or ranged attacks.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Ranged and melee attackers are shocked for <span class="d3-color-green">189%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the Arcane Power cost of all skills by <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> while Storm Armor is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Critical Hits have a chance to electrocute a nearby enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">425%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"lit",c:"lit",d:"lit",e:"lit",x:"lit"},icon:3537432142,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3537432142\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Bathe yourself in electrical energy, periodically shocking a nearby enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">175%</span> weapon damage as Lightning. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Armor may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Conjuration</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},teleport:{a:'<p>Cast a short range Wave of Force upon arrival, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">175%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to all nearby enemies and stunning them for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Summon <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> decoys for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds after teleporting.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',c:'<p>For <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after you Teleport, you will take <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> less damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Casting Teleport again within <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds will instantly return you to your original location and set the remaining cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',e:'<p>After casting Teleport, you have <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to Teleport <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> additional time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"arc",c:"arc",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:2217412135,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2217412135\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">11</span> seconds</p><p>Teleport through the ether to the selected location up to <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> yards away.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},waveofforce:{a:'<p>Wave of Force repels projectiles back toward their shooter, knocks back nearby enemies and Slows them by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Wave of Force gains a <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Each enemy hit restores <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Arcane Power.</p><p>Wave of Force\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the damage to <span class="d3-color-green">475%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Each enemy hit increases the damage of your next Arcane spell by <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit deal <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> reduced damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"arc",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"arc",e:"arc",x:"arc"},icon:3303174543,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3303174543\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Arcane Power</p><p>Discharge a wave of pure energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">390%</span> weapon damage as Arcane to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="special">Force</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.wizard={arcanedynamo:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3581007607\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you cast a Signature spell, you gain a Flash of Insight. After <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Flashes of Insight, your next non-Signature spell deals <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> additional damage. </p><p>The following skills are Signature spells:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Magic Missile<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Shock Pulse<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Spectral Blade<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Electrocute</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Dare not to invoke the wrath of a Wizard. You are nothing more than a loose coalescence of dust before their ire, easily scattered at a whim.</div> </div>',astralpresence:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2573566218\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase your maximum Arcane Power by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> and Arcane Power regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">2.5</span> per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Feel the power in the veil that surrounds us—a thunder cloud ready to burst... a volcano about to erupt. Harness it, and you will be invincible." —Adria</div> </div>',audacity:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3723713922\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> additional damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Those who dare approach you do so at their own peril." —Valthek, High Councilor of the Vizjerei</div> </div>',blur:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3409609379\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Decrease damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">17%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Truly powerful Wizards have been known to turn their magic inward, transmuting the very composition of their own bodies for boundless energy and catlike reflexes.</div> </div>',coldblooded:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1475200540\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Enemies chilled or frozen by you take <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> more damage from all sources for the duration of the chill or Freeze.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Feel your blood run cold as the water of the Frozen Sea, and know that I can shatter you with a touch." —The Ice Queen\'s Tale</div> </div>',conflagration:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1028263253\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Fire damage dealt to enemies applies a burning effect, increasing their chance to be critically hit by <span class="d3-color-green">6%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The red hot armor seared their flesh and boiled their blood as they tried desperately to pry it from smoldering bodies. We finished the defenseless creatures as an act of mercy." —Tales of Caldeum, Volume XII</div> </div>',dominance:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2864652961\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Killing an enemy grants a shield that absorbs <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> of your Life in damage for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. This effect can stack up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> times.</p><p>Refreshing Dominance will set the shield to its maximum possible potency and each stack will increase its total duration by <span class="d3-color-green">0.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Why waste your own energy? Using your enemy\'s to protect yourself strengthens you while it weakens him. What could be more perfect?" —Ennead Sage Resko</div> </div>',elementalexposure:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2137259648\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Damaging enemies with Arcane, Cold, Fire or Lightning will cause them to take <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> more damage from your attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Each different damage type applies a stack, stacking up to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> times.</p><p>Elemental damage from your weapon contributes to Elemental Exposure.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Adding insult to injury may be entertaining, but adding increased injury is a more effective tactic.</div> </div>',evocation:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4058933168\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce all cooldowns by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">So long have you focused on twisting reality to your will that time itself seeks to appease you.</div> </div>',galvanizingward:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1488020096\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>As long as you have not taken damage in the last <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds you gain a protective shield that absorbs the next <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> of your Life in damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Power begets power. The excess energy from one spell is absorbed by the other, and so the effect is sustained." —Excerpt from Grand Master Clavaught\'s Lecture on Synergistic Effects in Esoteric Arcane Spheres</div> </div>',glasscannon:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3607063845\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase all damage done by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>, but decrease Armor and resistances by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"How will I survive? I don\'t intend to get hit in the first place. If you even touch me, it\'s because I allowed it." —Maloth, renegade wizard</div> </div>',illusionist:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/860941742\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you take more than <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of your maximum Life in damage within <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second, the cooldowns on Mirror Image, Slow Time, and Teleport are reset.</p><p>When you use Mirror Image, Slow Time, or Teleport, your movement speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"To be where you are not is the wisest of strategies." —Grand Archmage Ralhys</div> </div>',paralysis:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3599231238\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Lightning spells have a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance to Stun all targets hit for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Some people are shocked by my mastery of magic." —Larra Stormlash</div> </div>',powerhungry:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1017338247\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> additional damage to enemies farther than <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"It just doesn\'t sit right with me. Some of the things these so-called wizards do... They border on necromancy. Or worse! It\'s just not proper magic." —Venerable Sorcerer Fob Dunar</div> </div>',prodigy:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3397625047\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you cast a Signature spell, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Arcane Power.</p><p>The following skills are Signature spells:<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Magic Missile<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Shock Pulse<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Spectral Blade<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Electrocute</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Heavy steel armor may turn aside a blade, but let\'s see how well it works against lightning!" —Larra Stormlash\'s infamous faux pas at the Royal Westmarch Joust</div> </div>',temporalflux:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/225438545\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Enemies that take Arcane damage are slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The energies of time and arcane power are jealous consorts. If you caress the one, you neglect the other at great risk." —Ennead Sage Resko</div> </div>',unstableanomaly:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4077865334\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you receive fatal damage, you instead gain a shield equal to <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> of your maximum Life for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds and release a shockwave that knocks enemies back and Stuns them for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. </p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"It takes perfect concentration for a Wizard to dance on the edge of infinity. Never be the one to break that concentration." —One-Eye Whipple</div> </div>',unwaveringwill:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/859252908\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Standing still for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds increases the following attributes:</p><p><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Armor: <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span><br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> All Resistances: <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span><br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> Damage: <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span></p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"At times the greatest strategy is to withdraw into yourself, to experience the clarity of mind in the moments before launching your attack." —Archmage Skye</div> </div>'};DiabloCalc.statLimits={rare:{attrLarge:{min:525,max:625},attrSmall:{min:350,max:415},attrVeryLarge:{min:788,max:945},armorSmall:{min:340,max:364},armorMedium:{min:340,max:545},armorLarge:{min:509,max:545},resistAll:{min:86,max:90},resistSingle:{min:121,max:140},lifeSmall:{min:8,max:14},lifeMedium:{min:8,max:16},lifeLarge:{min:12,max:16},iasNormal:{min:5,max:6},iasQuiver:{min:15,max:15},chcSmall:{min:4.5,max:6,step:.5},chcLarge:{min:8,max:10,step:.5},chdSmall:{min:26,max:50},chdLarge:{min:51,max:100},cdrSmall:{min:4,max:7},rcrSmall:{min:4,max:7},cdrLarge:{min:5,max:9},rcrLarge:{min:5,max:9},edmgSmall:{min:5,max:8},edmgLarge:{min:8,max:9},sockets1:{min:1,max:1},sockets2:{min:1,max:2},sockets3:{min:1,max:3},sockets4:{min:1,max:4},sockets5:{min:1,max:5},sockets6:{min:1,max:6},pickupNormal:{min:1,max:2},regenSmall:{m